90 gentity_t *INDEXENT(const int _gameId)
91 {
92  if (_gameId >= 0 && _gameId < MAX_GENTITIES)
93  {
94  switch (_gameId)
95  {
96  case ENTITYNUM_WORLD: // world ent not marked inuse for some reason
97  return &g_entities[ENTITYNUM_WORLD];
98  default:
99  return g_entities[_gameId].inuse ? &g_entities[_gameId] : 0;
100  }
101  }
102  return 0;
103 }
104 
105 int ENTINDEX(gentity_t *_ent)
106 {
107  return _ent - g_entities;
108 }

110 gentity_t *EntityFromHandle(GameEntity _ent)
111 {
112  obint16 index = _ent.GetIndex();
113  if ((unsigned)(int)index < MAX_GENTITIES)
114  {
115  if (m_EntityHandles[index].m_HandleSerial == _ent.GetSerial())
116  {
117  gentity_t *pEnt = &g_entities[index];
118  if (pEnt->inuse)
119  {
120  return pEnt;
121  }
122  }
123  if (index == ENTITYNUM_WORLD)
124  {
125  return &g_entities[ENTITYNUM_WORLD];
126  }
127  }
128  return NULL;
129 }
130 
131 GameEntity HandleFromEntity(gentity_t *_ent)
132 {
133  if (_ent)
134  {
135  return GameEntity(_ent - g_entities, m_EntityHandles[_ent - g_entities].m_HandleSerial);
136  }
137  else
138  {
139  return GameEntity();
140  }
141 }

151 void AddDeferredGoal(gentity_t *ent)
152 {
153  if (g_NumDeferredGoals >= MaxDeferredGoals - 1)
154  {
155  G_Error("Deferred Goal Buffer Full!");
156  return;
157  }
158 
159  MapGoalDef &goaldef = g_DeferredGoals[g_NumDeferredGoals++];
160  MapGoalDef &goaldef2 = g_DeferredGoals[g_NumDeferredGoals++];
161 
162  switch (ent->s.eType)
163  {
164  case ET_MG42_BARREL:
165  {
166  goaldef.Props.SetString("Type", "mountmg42");
167  goaldef.Props.SetEntity("Entity", HandleFromEntity(ent));
168  goaldef.Props.SetInt("Team", (1 << ET_TEAM_ALLIES) | (1 << ET_TEAM_AXIS));
169  goaldef.Props.SetString("TagName", _GetEntityName(ent));
170  goaldef.Props.SetInt("InterfaceGoal", 1);
171 
172  // cs: this was done in et_goalmanager before
173  goaldef2.Props.SetString("Type", "repairmg42");
174  goaldef2.Props.SetEntity("Entity", HandleFromEntity(ent));
175  goaldef2.Props.SetInt("Team", (1 << ET_TEAM_ALLIES) | (1 << ET_TEAM_AXIS));
176  goaldef2.Props.SetString("TagName", _GetEntityName(ent));
177  goaldef2.Props.SetInt("InterfaceGoal", 1);
178  break;
179  }
180  default:
181  {
182  break;
183  }
184  }
185 }

214 struct mg42s_t

223 mg42s_t mg42s[64];
224 int numofmg42s;
225 
226 void GetMG42s()
227 {
228  numofmg42s = 0;
229  gentity_t *trav = NULL;
230  char *name;
231 
232  while ((trav = G_Find(trav, FOFS(classname), "misc_mg42")) != NULL && numofmg42s < 64)
233  {
234  mg42s_t& mg42 = mg42s[numofmg42s++];
235  mg42.ent = trav;
236  GetEntityCenter(trav, mg42.position);
237 
238  name = (char *)_GetEntityName(trav);
239  if (name)
240  {
241  Q_strncpyz(mg42s[0].name, name, sizeof(mg42s[0].name));
242  }
243  else
244  {
245  mg42.name[0] = (char)0;
246  }
247 
248  mg42.buildable = false;
249  }
250 }
251 
252 void UpdateMG42(gentity_t *ent)
253 {
254  vec3_t entpos;
255 
256  for (int i = 0; i < numofmg42s; ++i)
257  {
258  if (mg42s[i].ent == ent)
259  {
260  return;
261  }
262  }
263 
264  GetEntityCenter(ent, entpos);
265 
266  for (int i = 0 ; i < numofmg42s ; ++i)
267  {
268  if (mg42s[i].position[0] == entpos[0] &&
269  mg42s[i].position[1] == entpos[1])
270  {
271  mg42s[i].ent = ent;
272  }
273  }
274 }
275 
276 void CheckForMG42(gentity_t *ent, const char *newname)
277 {
278  if (!numofmg42s)
279  {
280  return;
281  }
282 
283  vec3_t entpos;
284 
285  GetEntityCenter(ent, entpos);
286 
287  for (int i = 0 ; i < numofmg42s ; ++i)
288  {
289  if ((fabs(mg42s[i].position[0] - entpos[0]) < 100.0) &&
290  (fabs(mg42s[i].position[1] - entpos[1]) < 100.0))
291  {
292  mg42s[i].buildable = true;
293  Q_strncpyz(mg42s[i].newname, newname, sizeof(mg42s[0].newname));
294  }
295  }
296 
297  return;
298 }
299 
300 void GetEntityCenter(gentity_t *ent, vec3_t pos)
301 {
302  pos[0] = ent->r.currentOrigin[0] + ((ent->r.maxs[0] + ent->r.mins[0]) * 0.5f);
303  pos[1] = ent->r.currentOrigin[1] + ((ent->r.maxs[1] + ent->r.mins[1]) * 0.5f);
304  pos[2] = ent->r.currentOrigin[2] + ((ent->r.maxs[2] + ent->r.mins[2]) * 0.5f);
305 }

310 // Important note:
311 // These weaponcharged values are intentionally set a little bit lower
312 // so the bots can start heading towards a goal a bit ahead of time rather than waiting
313 // for a full charge. Have a look at NQ case WP_LANDMINE as an exmaple.
314 // Exception:
315 // In case of no goal is used (f.e. the riffle WP_GPG40 & WP_M7)
316 // we do an exact match instead of lowered value
317 // Note:
318 // There is a seperate goal for soldiers with panzer/bazooka to go defend at
319 static qboolean weaponCharged(playerState_t *ps, team_t team, int weapon, int *skill)
320 {
321  switch (weapon)
322  {
323 #if defined(NOQUARTER) || defined(LEGACY)
324  // IRATA added BAZOOKA
325  case WP_BAZOOKA:
326 #endif
327  case WP_PANZERFAUST:
328  if (ps->eFlags & EF_PRONE)
329  {
330  return qfalse;
331  }
332  if (skill[SK_HEAVY_WEAPONS] >= 1)
333  {
334  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_SOLDIER_TIME * 0.66f)
335  {
336  return qfalse;
337  }
338  }
339  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_SOLDIER_TIME)
340  {
341  return qfalse;
342  }
343  break;
344  case WP_MORTAR:
345  case WP_MORTAR_SET:
346 #if defined(NOQUARTER) || defined(LEGACY)
347  case WP_MORTAR2:
348  case WP_MORTAR2_SET:
349 #endif
350  if (skill[SK_HEAVY_WEAPONS] >= 1)
351  {
352  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_SOLDIER_TIME * 0.33f)
353  {
354  return qfalse;
355  }
356  }
357  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_SOLDIER_TIME * 0.5f)
358  {
359  return qfalse;
360  }
361  break;
362  case WP_SMOKE_BOMB:
363  case WP_SATCHEL:
364  if (skill[SK_MILITARY_INTELLIGENCE_AND_SCOPED_WEAPONS] >= 2)
365  {
366  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_COVERTOPS_TIME * 0.66f)
367  {
368  return qfalse;
369  }
370  }
371  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_COVERTOPS_TIME)
372  {
373  return qfalse;
374  }
375  break;
376  case WP_LANDMINE:
377 #ifdef NOQUARTER
378  // IRATA NQ: see bg_misc charge cost
379  // { 0.5f, 0.5f, 0.5f, .33f, .33f, .33f, .33f, .25f, .25f, .25f}; <--
380  if (skill[SK_EXPLOSIVES_AND_CONSTRUCTION] >= 2 && skill[SK_EXPLOSIVES_AND_CONSTRUCTION] <= 5)
381  {
382  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < (WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.33f))
383  {
384  return qfalse;
385  }
386  }
387  if (skill[SK_EXPLOSIVES_AND_CONSTRUCTION] >= 6 && skill[SK_EXPLOSIVES_AND_CONSTRUCTION] <= 9)
388  {
389  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < (WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.25f))
390  {
391  return qfalse;
392  }
393  }
394  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < (WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.5f))
395  {
396  return qfalse;
397  }
398 #else
399  if (skill[SK_EXPLOSIVES_AND_CONSTRUCTION] >= 2)
400  {
401  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < (WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.33f))
402  {
403  return qfalse;
404  }
405  }
406  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < (WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.5f))
407  {
408  return qfalse;
409  }
410 #endif
411  break;
412  case WP_DYNAMITE:
413  if (skill[SK_EXPLOSIVES_AND_CONSTRUCTION] >= 3)
414  {
415  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < (WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.66f))
416  {
417  return qfalse;
418  }
419  }
420  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_ENGINEER_TIME)
421  {
422  return qfalse;
423  }
424  break;
425  case WP_MEDKIT:
426  if (skill[SK_FIRST_AID] >= 2)
427  {
428  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_MEDIC_TIME * 0.15f)
429  {
430  return qfalse;
431  }
432  }
433  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_MEDIC_TIME * 0.25f)
434  {
435  return qfalse;
436  }
437  break;
438  case WP_AMMO:
439  if (skill[SK_SIGNALS] >= 1)
440  {
441  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_FIELDOPS_TIME * 0.15f)
442  {
443  return qfalse;
444  }
445  }
446  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_FIELDOPS_TIME * 0.25f)
447  {
448  return qfalse;
449  }
450  break;
451  case WP_SMOKE_MARKER:
452  if (skill[SK_SIGNALS] >= 2)
453  {
454  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_FIELDOPS_TIME * 0.66f)
455  {
456  return qfalse;
457  }
458  }
459  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_FIELDOPS_TIME)
460  {
461  return qfalse;
462  }
463  break;
464  case WP_MEDIC_ADRENALINE:
465 #ifdef NOQUARTER
466  //cs: from BG_CheckCharge()
467  if (ps->powerups[PW_ADRENALINE])
468  {
469  return qfalse;
470  }
471 #else
472  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_MEDIC_TIME)
473  {
474  return qfalse;
475  }
476 #endif
477  break;
478  case WP_BINOCULARS:
479  switch (ps->stats[STAT_PLAYER_CLASS])
480  {
481  case PC_FIELDOPS:
482  if (skill[SK_SIGNALS] >= 2)
483  {
484  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT <= WC_FIELDOPS_TIME * 0.66f)
485  {
486  return qfalse;
487  }
488  }
489  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT <= WC_FIELDOPS_TIME)
490  {
491  return qfalse;
492  }
493  break;
494  default:
495  return qfalse;
496  }
497  break;
498  case WP_GPG40:
499  case WP_M7:
500 #ifdef NOQUARTER
501  // IRATA NQ: see bg_misc charge cost
502  //{ .50f, .50f, .50f, .50f, .50f, .50f, .50f, .50f, .35f, .35f};
503  if (skill[SK_EXPLOSIVES_AND_CONSTRUCTION] >= 8)
504  {
505  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.35f)
506  {
507  return qfalse;
508  }
509  }
510  else if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.5f)
511  {
512  return qfalse;
513  }
514 #else
515  if (WC_WEAPON_TIME_LEFT < WC_ENGINEER_TIME * 0.5f)
516  {
517  return qfalse;
518  }
519 #endif
520  break;
521  }
522  return qtrue;
523 }

525 // cs: added ignore ent so the bot wont count itself.
526 // this fixes soldier counts since latchPlayerType defaults to 0
527 static int CountPlayerClass(team_t team, int playerClass, int ignore)
528 {
529  int num = 0;
530  int j;
531 
532  for (int i = 0; i < level.numConnectedClients; ++i)
533  {
534  if (i == ignore)
535  {
536  continue;
537  }
538 
539  j = level.sortedClients[i];
540 
541  if (level.clients[j].sess.sessionTeam != team)
542  {
543  continue;
544  }
545 
546  if (level.clients[j].sess.latchPlayerType != playerClass)
547  {
548  continue;
549  }
550  num++;
551  }
552  return num;
553 }

555 int Bot_TeamGameToBot(int team)

561  case TEAM_ALLIES:

563  case TEAM_SPECTATOR:

565  default:
566  return ET_TEAM_NONE;

568 }

570 static int playerClassBotToGame(int playerClass)
571 {
572  switch (playerClass)
573  {
574  case ET_CLASS_SOLDIER:
575  return PC_SOLDIER;
576  case ET_CLASS_MEDIC:
577  return PC_MEDIC;
578  case ET_CLASS_ENGINEER:
579  return PC_ENGINEER;
580  case ET_CLASS_FIELDOPS:
581  return PC_FIELDOPS;
582  case ET_CLASS_COVERTOPS:
583  return PC_COVERTOPS;
584  default:
585  return -1;
586  }
587 }

1040 qboolean Simple_EmplacedGunIsRepairable(gentity_t *ent)
1041 {
1042  if (Q_stricmp(ent->classname, "misc_mg42") /*&& Q_stricmp( ent->classname, "misc_aagun" )*/)
1043  {
1044  return qfalse;
1045  }
1046  if (ent->s.frame == 0)
1047  {
1048  return qfalse;
1049  }
1050  return qtrue;
1051 }

1561 static void ReTransmitWeapons(const gentity_t *bot)
1562 {
1563  if (!bot || !bot->client)
1564  {
1565  return;
1566  }
1567 
1568  Bot_Event_ResetWeapons(bot - g_entities);
1569 
1570  for (int weapon = WP_NONE + 1; weapon < WP_NUM_WEAPONS; ++weapon)
1571  {
1572  if (COM_BitCheck(bot->client->ps.weapons, weapon))
1573  {
1574  Bot_Event_AddWeapon(bot - g_entities, Bot_WeaponGameToBot(weapon));
1575  }
1576  }
1577 }

1579 #define MAX_SMOKE_RADIUS 320.0f
1580 #define MAX_SMOKE_RADIUS_TIME 10000.0f
1581 #define UNAFFECTED_BY_SMOKE_DIST Square(100)
1582 
1583 gentity_t *Bot_EntInvisibleBySmokeBomb(vec3_t start, vec3_t end)
1584 {
1585  // if the target is close enough, vision is not affected by smoke bomb
1586  if (DistanceSquared(start, end) < UNAFFECTED_BY_SMOKE_DIST)
1587  {
1588  //pfnPrintMessage("within unaffected dist");
1589  return 0;
1590  }
1591 
1592  gentity_t *ent = NULL;
1593  vec3_t smokeCenter;
1594  float smokeRadius;
1595 
1596  //while (ent = G_FindSmokeBomb( ent ))
1597  for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SMOKEGREN_CACHE; ++i)
1598  {
1599  ent = g_SmokeGrenadeCache[i];
1600  if (!ent)
1601  {
1602  continue;
1603  }
1604 
1605 #ifdef LEGACY
1606  if (!ent->s.effect1Time)
1607 #else
1608  if (ent->s.effect1Time == 16)
1609 #endif
1610  {
1611  //pfnPrintMessage("smoke not up yet");
1612  // xkan, the smoke has not really started yet, see weapon_smokeBombExplode
1613  // and CG_RenderSmokeGrenadeSmoke
1614  continue;
1615  }
1616  // check the distance
1617  VectorCopy(ent->s.pos.trBase, smokeCenter);
1618  // raise the center to better match the position of the smoke, see
1619  // CG_SpawnSmokeSprite().
1620  smokeCenter[2] += 32;
1621  // smoke sprite has a maximum radius of 640/2. and it takes a while for it to
1622  // reach that size, so adjust the radius accordingly.
1623  smokeRadius = MAX_SMOKE_RADIUS * ((level.time - ent->grenadeExplodeTime) / MAX_SMOKE_RADIUS_TIME);
1624  if (smokeRadius > MAX_SMOKE_RADIUS)
1625  {
1626  smokeRadius = MAX_SMOKE_RADIUS;
1627  }
1628  // if distance from line is short enough, vision is blocked by smoke
1629 
1630  if (DistanceFromLineSquared(smokeCenter, start, end) < (smokeRadius * smokeRadius))
1631  {
1633 
1634  //const float DistToEnd = VectorDistanceSquared(start,end);
1635  //const float DistToSmoke = VectorDistanceSquared(start,smokeCenter);
1636 
1637  //g_InterfaceFunctions->DebugLine(smokeCenter, end,obColor(0,255,0),0.2f);
1638  //pfnPrintMessage("hid by smoke");
1639  return ent;
1640  }
1641  //pfnAddTempDisplayLine(smokeCenter, start, fColorRed);
1642  //g_InterfaceFunctions->DebugLine(smokeCenter, end,obColor(255,0,0),0.2f);
1643  }
1644 
1645  return 0;
1646 }

1648 void Bot_Util_AddGoal(const char *_type, gentity_t *_ent, int _team, const char *_tag, const char *_extrakey = 0, obUserData *_extraval = 0)
1649 {
1650  if (IsOmnibotLoaded())
1651  {
1652  MapGoalDef goaldef;
1653 
1654  goaldef.Props.SetString("Type", _type);
1655  goaldef.Props.SetEntity("Entity", HandleFromEntity(_ent));
1656  goaldef.Props.SetInt("Team", _team);
1657  goaldef.Props.SetString("TagName", _tag);
1658  goaldef.Props.SetInt("InterfaceGoal", 1);
1659  if (_extrakey && _extraval)
1660  {
1661  goaldef.Props.Set(_extrakey, *_extraval);
1662  }
1663  g_BotFunctions.pfnAddGoal(goaldef);
1664  }
1665 }

1667 static int _GetEntityTeam(gentity_t *_ent)
1668 {
1669  // FIXME: hack, when the game joins clients again after warmup, they are temporarily ET_GENERAL entities(LAME)
1670  if (_ent->client && (_ent - g_entities) < MAX_CLIENTS)
1671  {
1672  //t = ET_PLAYER;
1673  return Bot_TeamGameToBot(_ent->client->sess.sessionTeam);
1674  }
1675 
1676  int t = _ent->s.eType;
1677 
1678  switch (t)
1679  {
1680  case ET_PLAYER:
1681  if (_ent->client)
1682  {
1683  return Bot_TeamGameToBot(_ent->client->sess.sessionTeam);
1684  }
1685  break;
1686  case ET_CORPSE:
1687  return Bot_TeamGameToBot(BODY_TEAM(_ent));
1688 #ifndef LEGACY
1689  case ET_MISSILE:
1690  if (_ent->s.weapon == WP_LANDMINE || _ent->s.weapon == WP_DYNAMITE)
1691  {
1692  return Bot_TeamGameToBot(G_LandmineTeam(_ent));
1693  }
1694 #endif
1695  // Let this fall through
1696  default:
1697  return Bot_TeamGameToBot(_ent->s.teamNum);
1698  }
1699 
1700  return 0;
1701 }

1703 static int _GetEntityClass(gentity_t *_ent)
1704 {
1705  // hack, when the game joins clients again after warmup, they are temporarily ET_GENERAL entities(LAME)
1706  int t = _ent->s.eType;
1707  if (_ent->client && (_ent - g_entities) < MAX_CLIENTS)
1708  {
1709  t = ET_PLAYER;
1710  }
1711 
1712  switch (t)
1713  {
1714  case ET_GENERAL:
1715  {
1716  if (!Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "func_invisible_user"))
1717  {
1718  return ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_BUTTON;
1719  }
1720  else if (!Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "func_button"))
1721  {
1722  return ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_BUTTON;
1723  }
1724  else if (!Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "misc_mg42"))
1725  {
1726  return ET_CLASSEX_MG42MOUNT;
1727  }
1728  else if (!Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "props_chair_hiback"))
1729  {
1730  return ET_CLASSEX_BROKENCHAIR;
1731  }
1732  else if (!Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "props_chair"))
1733  {
1734  return ET_CLASSEX_BROKENCHAIR;
1735  }
1736  else if (!Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "props_chair_side"))
1737  {
1738  return ET_CLASSEX_BROKENCHAIR;
1739  }
1740  // cs: waypoint tool, don't merge the spawns
1741  else if (!Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "info_player_deathmatch") ||
1742  !Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "team_CTF_redspawn") ||
1743  !Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "team_CTF_bluespawn") ||
1744  !Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "info_player_spawn"))
1745  {
1746  return ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_PLAYERSTART;
1747  }
1748  break;
1749  }
1750  case ET_INVISIBLE:
1751  {
1752  if (_ent->client)
1753  {
1754  return ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_SPECTATOR;
1755  }
1756  break;
1757  }
1758  case ET_PLAYER:
1759  {
1760  if (!_ent->client || (_ent->entstate == STATE_INVISIBLE) ||
1761  (_ent->client->sess.sessionTeam != TEAM_AXIS &&
1762  _ent->client->sess.sessionTeam != TEAM_ALLIES))
1763  {
1764  return ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_SPECTATOR;
1765  }
1766 
1767  // Special case for dead players that haven't respawned.
1768  /*if(_ent->health <= 0 && _ent->client->ps.pm_type == PM_DEAD)
1769  return ET_CLASSEX_INJUREDPLAYER;*/
1770 
1771  // for scripted class changes, count latched in warmup or if dead
1772  /*if ( g_gamestate.integer > GS_PLAYING
1773  || _ent->client->ps.pm_type > PM_SPECTATOR
1774  || _ent->client->ps.pm_flags & PMF_LIMBO )
1775  return Bot_PlayerClassGameToBot(_ent->client->sess.latchPlayerType);*/
1776 
1777  return Bot_PlayerClassGameToBot(_ent->client->sess.latchPlayerType);
1778  }
1779  case ET_ITEM:
1780  {
1781  if (!Q_strncmp(_ent->classname, "item_health", 11))
1782  {
1783  return ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_HEALTH;
1784  }
1785  else if (!Q_strncmp(_ent->classname, "weapon_magicammo", 16))
1786  {
1787  return ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_AMMO;
1788  }
1789  else if (!Q_stricmp(_ent->classname, "item_treasure"))
1790  {
1791  return ET_CLASSEX_TREASURE;
1792  }
1793  else if (_ent->item && _ent->item->giType == IT_WEAPON)
1794  {
1795  return ET_CLASSEX_WEAPON + Bot_WeaponGameToBot(_ent->item->giWeapon);
1796  }
1797  break;
1798  }
1799  case ET_CORPSE:
1800  {
1801  return ET_CLASSEX_CORPSE;
1802  }
1803  case ET_MISSILE:
1804  {
1805  // Register certain weapons as threats to avoid or whatever.
1806  switch (_ent->s.weapon)
1807  {
1808  case WP_GRENADE_LAUNCHER:

1810  return ET_CLASSEX_GRENADE;

1813 #if defined(NOQUARTER) || defined(LEGACY)

1956 qboolean _TankIsMountable(gentity_t *_ent)
1957 {
1958  if (!(_ent->spawnflags & 128))
1959  {
1960  return qfalse;
1961  }
1962 
1963  if (level.disableTankEnter)
1964  {
1965  return qfalse;
1966  }
1967 
1968  /*if( G_TankIsOccupied( ent ) )
1969  return qfalse;*/
1970  if (g_OmniBotFlags.integer & OBF_DONT_MOUNT_TANKS)
1971  {
1972  return qfalse;
1973  }
1974 
1975  if (_ent->health <= 0)
1976  {
1977  return qfalse;
1978  }
1979 
1980  return qtrue;
1981 }

2004 int obUtilBotContentsFromGameContents(int _contents)

2012  {
2013  iBotContents |= CONT_WATER;
2014  }
2015  if (_contents & CONTENTS_SLIME)
2016  {
2017  iBotContents |= CONT_SLIME;
2018  }
2019  if (_contents & CONTENTS_FOG)
2020  {
2021  iBotContents |= CONT_FOG;
2022  }
2023  if (_contents & CONTENTS_TELEPORTER)
2024  {
2025  iBotContents |= CONT_TELEPORTER;
2026  }
2027  if (_contents & CONTENTS_MOVER)
2028  {
2029  iBotContents |= CONT_MOVER;
2030  }
2031  if (_contents & CONTENTS_TRIGGER)
2032  {
2033  iBotContents |= CONT_TRIGGER;
2034  }
2035  if (_contents & CONTENTS_LAVA)
2036  {
2037  iBotContents |= CONT_LAVA;
2038  }
2039  if (_contents & CONTENTS_PLAYERCLIP)
2040  {
2041  iBotContents |= CONT_PLYRCLIP;
2042  }
2043  return iBotContents;
2044 }

2060 void Bot_Util_CheckForGoalEntity(GameEntity _ent)
2061 {
2062  if (IsOmnibotLoaded())
2063  {
2064  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
2065 
2066  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse)
2067  {
2068  switch (pEnt->s.eType)
2069  {
2070  case ET_ITEM:
2071  {
2072  char buffer[256] = { 0 };
2073  const char *pGoalName = _GetEntityName(pEnt);
2074 
2075  if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "team_CTF_redflag"))
2076  {
2077  // allies flag
2078  if (pEnt->s.otherEntityNum != -1)
2079  {
2080  pGoalName = _GetEntityName(&g_entities[pEnt->s.otherEntityNum]);
2081  }
2082  sprintf(buffer, "%s_dropped", pGoalName ? pGoalName : "allies_flag");
2083  Bot_Util_AddGoal("flag", pEnt, (1 << ET_TEAM_ALLIES), buffer);
2084  Bot_Util_AddGoal("flagreturn", pEnt, (1 << ET_TEAM_AXIS), buffer);
2085  }
2086  else if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "team_CTF_blueflag"))
2087  {
2088  // axis flag
2089  if (pEnt->s.otherEntityNum != -1)
2090  {
2091  pGoalName = _GetEntityName(&g_entities[pEnt->s.otherEntityNum]);
2092  }
2093  sprintf(buffer, "%s_dropped", pGoalName ? pGoalName : "axis_flag");
2094  Bot_Util_AddGoal("flag", pEnt, (1 << ET_TEAM_AXIS), buffer);
2095  Bot_Util_AddGoal("flagreturn", pEnt, (1 << ET_TEAM_ALLIES), buffer);
2096  }
2097  break;
2098  }
2099  default:
2100  break;
2101  }
2102  }
2103  }
2104 }
2105 
2106 // helper stuff
2107 qboolean InFieldOfVision(vec3_t viewangles, float fov, vec3_t angles)
2108 {
2109  float diff, angle;
2110 
2111  for (int i = 0; i < 2; ++i)
2112  {
2113  angle = AngleMod(viewangles[i]);
2114  angles[i] = AngleMod(angles[i]);
2115  diff = angles[i] - angle;
2116  if (angles[i] > angle)
2117  {
2118  if (diff > 180.0)
2119  {
2120  diff -= 360.0;
2121  }
2122  }
2123  else
2124  {
2125  if (diff < -180.0)
2126  {
2127  diff += 360.0;
2128  }
2129  }
2130  if (diff > 0)
2131  {
2132  if (diff > fov * 0.5)
2133  {
2134  return qfalse;
2135  }
2136  }
2137  else
2138  {
2139  if (diff < -fov * 0.5)
2140  {
2141  return qfalse;
2142  }
2143  }
2144  }
2145  return qtrue;
2146 }

2168

2179 #endif

2193  void RemoveBot(const MessageHelper &_data)
2194  {
2195  OB_GETMSG(Msg_Kickbot);
2196  if (pMsg->m_GameId != Msg_Kickbot::InvalidGameId)
2197  {

2199  {
2200  gentity_t *ent = &g_entities[pMsg->m_GameId];
2201  if (IsBot(ent))
2202  {
2203  trap_DropClient(pMsg->m_GameId, "disconnected", 0);
2204  }
2205  }
2206  }
2207  else
2208  {
2209  char cleanNetName[MAX_NETNAME];
2210  char cleanName[MAX_NAME_LENGTH];
2211 
2212  Q_strncpyz(cleanName, pMsg->m_Name, MAX_NAME_LENGTH);
2213  Q_CleanStr(cleanName);
2214 
2215  for (int i = 0; i < g_maxclients.integer; ++i)
2216  {
2217  if (!g_entities[i].inuse)
2218  {
2219  continue;
2220  }
2221  if (!IsBot(&g_entities[i]))
2222  {
2223  continue;
2224  }
2225 
2226  // clean stuff
2227  Q_strncpyz(cleanNetName, g_entities[i].client->pers.netname, MAX_NETNAME);
2228  Q_CleanStr(cleanNetName);
2229 
2230  if (!Q_stricmp(cleanNetName, cleanName))
2231  {
2232  trap_DropClient(i, "disconnected", 0);
2233  }
2234  }
2235  }
2236  }

2563  void UpdateBotInput(int _client, const ClientInput &_input)
2564  {
2565  static usercmd_t cmd;
2566  gentity_t *bot = &g_entities[_client];
2567 
2568  // only causes problems
2569  bot->client->ps.pm_flags &= ~PMF_RESPAWNED;
2570 
2571  Com_Memset(&cmd, 0, sizeof(cmd));
2572 
2573  cmd.identClient = _client;
2574  cmd.serverTime = level.time;
2575 
2576  // Set the weapon
2577  cmd.weapon = _weaponBotToGame(_input.m_CurrentWeapon);
2578 
2579 #if defined(NOQUARTER) || defined(LEGACY)
2580  // cs: nq bots need to select alt versions of mobile mg and mortar
2581  if (bot->client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_ALLIES)
2582  {
2583  if (cmd.weapon == WP_MOBILE_MG42)
2584  {
2585  cmd.weapon = WP_MOBILE_BROWNING;
2586  }
2587  else if (cmd.weapon == WP_MOBILE_MG42_SET)
2588  {
2589  cmd.weapon = WP_MOBILE_BROWNING_SET;
2590  }
2591  else if (cmd.weapon == WP_KNIFE)
2592  {
2593  cmd.weapon = WP_KNIFE_KABAR;
2594  }
2595 #ifdef LEGACY
2596  else if (cmd.weapon == WP_PANZERFAUST)
2597  {
2598  cmd.weapon = WP_BAZOOKA;
2599  }
2600 #endif
2601  }
2602  else if (bot->client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_AXIS)
2603  {
2604  if (cmd.weapon == WP_MORTAR)
2605  {
2606  cmd.weapon = WP_MORTAR2;
2607  }
2608  else if (cmd.weapon == WP_MORTAR_SET)
2609  {
2610  cmd.weapon = WP_MORTAR2_SET;
2611  }
2612  }
2613 #endif
2614 
2615  // dont choose scoped directly.
2616  switch (cmd.weapon)
2617  {
2618  case WP_GARAND_SCOPE:
2619  cmd.weapon = WP_GARAND;
2620  break;
2621  case WP_FG42SCOPE:
2622  cmd.weapon = WP_FG42;
2623  break;
2624  case WP_K43_SCOPE:
2625  cmd.weapon = WP_K43;
2626  break;
2627  }
2628 
2629  if (cmd.weapon == WP_BINOCULARS)
2630  {
2631  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_ZOOM;
2632  }
2633 
2634  // If trying to switch to rifle nade from anything other than the base rifle, switch to base first
2635 #if defined(NOQUARTER)
2636  if (cmd.weapon == WP_GPG40 && bot->client->ps.weapon == WP_GPG40 /*&& bot->client->ps.weapon != WP_KAR98*/)
2637  {
2638  const int ammo = bot->client->ps.ammoclip[WeaponTable[WP_GPG40].clipindex];
2639  if (ammo == 0 && bot->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_READY)
2640  {
2641  cmd.weapon = WP_KAR98;
2642  }
2643  }
2644  else if (cmd.weapon == WP_M7 && bot->client->ps.weapon == WP_M7 /*&& bot->client->ps.weapon != WP_CARBINE*/)
2645  {
2646  const int ammo = bot->client->ps.ammoclip[WeaponTable[WP_M7].clipindex];
2647  if (ammo == 0 && bot->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_READY)
2648  {
2649  cmd.weapon = WP_CARBINE;
2650  }
2651  }
2652  else if (cmd.weapon == WP_FOOTKICK)
2653  {
2654  // convert from weapon request to command
2655  cmd.buttons |= BUTTON_GESTURE;
2656  }
2657 #elif !defined (LEGACY)
2658  if (cmd.weapon == WP_GPG40 && bot->client->ps.weapon == WP_GPG40 /*&& bot->client->ps.weapon != WP_KAR98*/)
2659  {
2660  const int ammo = bot->client->ps.ammoclip[GetWeaponTableData(WP_GPG40)->clipIndex];
2661  if (ammo == 0 && bot->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_READY)
2662  {
2663  cmd.weapon = WP_KAR98;
2664  }
2665  }
2666  else if (cmd.weapon == WP_M7 && bot->client->ps.weapon == WP_M7 /*&& bot->client->ps.weapon != WP_CARBINE*/)
2667  {
2668  const int ammo = bot->client->ps.ammoclip[GetWeaponTableData(WP_M7)->clipIndex];
2669  if (ammo == 0 && bot->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_READY)
2670  {
2671  cmd.weapon = WP_CARBINE;
2672  }
2673  }
2674 #endif
2675 
2676  // Process the bot keypresses.
2677  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_RESPAWN))
2678  {
2679  cmd.buttons |= BUTTON_ACTIVATE;
2680  }
2681  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_ATTACK1))
2682  {
2683  cmd.buttons |= BUTTON_ATTACK;
2684  }
2685  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_WALK))
2686  {
2687  cmd.buttons |= BUTTON_WALKING;
2688  }
2689  else if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_SPRINT))
2690  {
2691  cmd.buttons |= BUTTON_SPRINT;
2692  }
2693  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_USE))
2694  {
2695  cmd.buttons |= BUTTON_ACTIVATE;
2696  }
2697 
2698  // wbuttons
2699  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_ATTACK2))
2700  {
2701  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_ATTACK2;
2702  }
2703 
2704  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_DROP))
2705  {
2706  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_DROP;
2707  }
2708 
2709  // if we have prone held
2710  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_PRONE))
2711  {
2712  // and we're not prone, go prone
2713  if (!(bot->client->ps.eFlags & EF_PRONE))
2714  {
2715  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_PRONE;
2716  }
2717  }
2718  else
2719  {
2720  // if prone is not held, and we're prone, exit prone
2721  if (bot->client->ps.eFlags & EF_PRONE)
2722  {
2723  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_PRONE;
2724  }
2725  }
2726 
2727  // if we have aim held
2728  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_AIM))
2729  {
2730  //if(!(bot->s.eFlags & EF_ZOOMING))
2731  switch (bot->client->ps.weapon)
2732  {
2733  case WP_GARAND:
2734  case WP_GARAND_SCOPE:
2735  cmd.weapon = WP_GARAND_SCOPE;
2736  break;
2737  case WP_FG42:
2738  case WP_FG42SCOPE:
2739  cmd.weapon = WP_FG42SCOPE;
2740  break;
2741  case WP_K43:
2742  case WP_K43_SCOPE:
2743  cmd.weapon = WP_K43_SCOPE;
2744  break;
2745  default:
2746  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_ZOOM;
2747  break;
2748  }
2749  }
2750  else
2751  {
2752  // if aim not held and we're zooming, zoom out.
2753  //if(bot->s.eFlags & EF_ZOOMING)
2754  //{
2755  // trap_EA_Command(_client, "-zoom");
2756  // //cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_ZOOM;
2757  //}
2758  }
2759 
2760  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_LEANLEFT))
2761  {
2762  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_LEANLEFT;
2763  }
2764  else if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_LEANRIGHT))
2765  {
2766  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_LEANRIGHT;
2767  }
2768 
2769  if (bot->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_DROPPING_TORELOAD ||
2770  bot->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_RELOADING ||
2771  bot->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_RAISING_TORELOAD)
2772  {
2773  // keep the same weapon while reloading
2774  cmd.weapon = bot->client->ps.weapon;
2775  }
2776  else if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_RELOAD))
2777  {
2778  // watch for gpg40 and m7 as these need to be switched for reloading
2779  /*switch(_input.m_CurrentWeapon)
2780  {
2781  case ET_WP_GPG40:
2782  cmd.weapon = _weaponBotToGame(ET_WP_KAR98);
2783  break;
2784  case ET_WP_M7:
2785  cmd.weapon = _weaponBotToGame(ET_WP_CARBINE);
2786  break;
2787  case ET_WP_GARAND_SCOPE:
2788  cmd.weapon = _weaponBotToGame(ET_WP_GARAND);
2789  break;
2790  case ET_WP_FG42_SCOPE:
2791  cmd.weapon = _weaponBotToGame(ET_WP_FG42);
2792  break;
2793  case ET_WP_K43_SCOPE:
2794  cmd.weapon = _weaponBotToGame(ET_WP_K43);
2795  break;
2796  default:
2797  break;
2798  }*/
2799  cmd.wbuttons |= WBUTTON_RELOAD;
2800  }
2801 
2802  // don't process view angles and moving stuff when dead
2803  if (bot->client->ps.pm_type >= PM_DEAD || bot->client->ps.pm_flags & (PMF_LIMBO | PMF_TIME_LOCKPLAYER))
2804  {
2805  // cant move in these states
2806  cmd.buttons &= ~BUTTON_ATTACK;
2807  cmd.wbuttons &= ~WBUTTON_ATTACK2;
2808 #ifdef NOQUARTER
2809  cmd.buttons &= ~BUTTON_GESTURE;
2810 #endif
2811  }
2812  else
2813  {
2814  float fMaxSpeed = 127.f;
2815  vec3_t angles, bodyangles, forward, right;
2816 
2817  // Convert the bots vector to angles and set the view angle to the orientation
2818  vectoangles(_input.m_Facing, angles);
2819  SetClientViewAngle(bot, angles);
2820 
2821  if (cmd.buttons & BUTTON_WALKING)
2822  {
2823  fMaxSpeed = 64.f;
2824  }
2825 
2826  // Convert the move direction into forward and right moves to
2827  // take the bots orientation into account.
2828 
2829  // flatten the view angles so we get a proper fwd,right vector as relevent to movement.
2830  VectorCopy(angles, bodyangles);
2831  bodyangles[PITCH] = 0;
2832 
2833  AngleVectors(bodyangles, forward, right, NULL);
2834  const float fwd = DotProduct(forward, _input.m_MoveDir);
2835  const float rght = DotProduct(right, _input.m_MoveDir);
2836 
2837  cmd.forwardmove = (char)(fwd * fMaxSpeed);
2838  cmd.rightmove = (char)(rght * fMaxSpeed);
2839 
2840  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_FWD) || _input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_MOVEUP))
2841  {
2842  cmd.forwardmove = (char)fMaxSpeed;
2843  }
2844  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_BACK) || _input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_MOVEDN))
2845  {
2846  cmd.forwardmove = (char)-fMaxSpeed;
2847  }
2848  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_RSTRAFE))
2849  {
2850  cmd.rightmove = (char)fMaxSpeed;
2851  }
2852  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_LSTRAFE))
2853  {
2854  cmd.rightmove = (char)-fMaxSpeed;
2855  }
2856  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_JUMP))
2857  {
2858  cmd.upmove = (char)fMaxSpeed;
2859  }
2860  if (_input.m_ButtonFlags.CheckFlag(BOT_BUTTON_CROUCH))
2861  {
2862  cmd.upmove = (char)-fMaxSpeed;
2863  }
2864  }
2865  trap_BotUserCommand(_client, &cmd);
2866  }

2878  obResult TraceLine(obTraceResult &_result, const float _start[3], const float _end[3],
2879  const AABB *_pBBox, int _mask, int _user, obBool _bUsePVS)
2880  {
2881  qboolean bInPVS = _bUsePVS ? trap_InPVS(_start, _end) : qtrue;
2882  if (bInPVS)
2883  {
2884  int iMask = 0;
2885 
2886  // Set up the collision masks
2887  if (_mask & TR_MASK_ALL)
2888  {
2889  iMask = MASK_ALL;
2890  }
2891  else
2892  {
2893  if (_mask & TR_MASK_SOLID)
2894  {
2895  iMask |= MASK_SOLID;
2896  }
2897  if (_mask & TR_MASK_PLAYER)
2898  {
2899  iMask |= MASK_PLAYERSOLID;
2900  }
2901  if (_mask & TR_MASK_SHOT)
2902  {
2903  iMask |= MASK_SHOT;
2904  }
2905  if (_mask & TR_MASK_OPAQUE)
2906  {
2907  iMask |= MASK_OPAQUE;
2908  }
2909  if (_mask & TR_MASK_WATER)
2910  {
2911  iMask |= MASK_WATER;
2912  }
2913  if (_mask & TR_MASK_PLAYERCLIP)
2914  {
2915  iMask |= CONTENTS_PLAYERCLIP;
2916  }
2917  if (_mask & (TR_MASK_FLOODFILL | TR_MASK_FLOODFILLENT))
2918  {
2919  iMask |= CONTENTS_PLAYERCLIP | CONTENTS_SOLID;
2920  }
2921 
2922  if (_mask & TR_MASK_SMOKEBOMB)
2923  {
2924  gentity_t *pSmokeBlocker = Bot_EntInvisibleBySmokeBomb((float *)_start, (float *)_end);
2925  if (pSmokeBlocker)
2926  {
2927  _result.m_Fraction = 0.0f;
2928  _result.m_HitEntity = HandleFromEntity(pSmokeBlocker);
2929  return Success;
2930  }
2931  }
2932  }
2933 
2934  trace_t tr;
2935 
2936  if (_mask & TR_MASK_FLOODFILL)
2937  {
2938  trap_TraceNoEnts(&tr, _start,
2939  _pBBox ? _pBBox->m_Mins : NULL,
2940  _pBBox ? _pBBox->m_Maxs : NULL,
2941  _end, _user, iMask);
2942  }
2943  else
2944  {
2945  trap_Trace(&tr, _start,
2946  _pBBox ? _pBBox->m_Mins : NULL,
2947  _pBBox ? _pBBox->m_Maxs : NULL,
2948  _end, _user, iMask);
2949  }
2950 
2951  if ((tr.entityNum != ENTITYNUM_WORLD) && (tr.entityNum != ENTITYNUM_NONE))
2952  {
2953  _result.m_HitEntity = HandleFromEntity(&g_entities[tr.entityNum]);
2954  }
2955  else
2956  {
2957  _result.m_HitEntity.Reset();
2958  }
2959 
2960  //_result.m_iUser1 = tr.surfaceFlags;
2961 
2962  // Fill in the bot traceflag.
2963  _result.m_Fraction = tr.fraction;
2964  _result.m_StartSolid = tr.startsolid;
2965  _result.m_Endpos[0] = tr.endpos[0];
2966  _result.m_Endpos[1] = tr.endpos[1];
2967  _result.m_Endpos[2] = tr.endpos[2];
2968  _result.m_Normal[0] = tr.plane.normal[0];
2969  _result.m_Normal[1] = tr.plane.normal[1];
2970  _result.m_Normal[2] = tr.plane.normal[2];
2971  _result.m_Contents = obUtilBotContentsFromGameContents(tr.contents);
2972  _result.m_Surface = obUtilBotSurfaceFromGameSurface(tr.surfaceFlags);
2973  }
2974  else
2975  {
2976  // Not in PVS
2977  _result.m_Fraction = 0.0f;
2978  _result.m_HitEntity.Reset();
2979  }
2980  return bInPVS ? Success : OutOfPVS;
2981  }

3249  obResult GetEntityCategory(const GameEntity _ent, BitFlag32 &_category)
3250  {
3251  obResult res = Success;
3252  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
3253 
3254  if (!pEnt)
3255  {
3256  return InvalidEntity;
3257  }
3258 
3259  // hack, when the game joins clients again after warmup, they are temporarily ET_GENERAL entities(LAME)
3260  int t = pEnt->s.eType;
3261  if (pEnt->client && (pEnt - g_entities) < MAX_CLIENTS)
3262  {
3263  t = ET_PLAYER;
3264  }
3265 
3266  switch (t)
3267  {
3268  case ET_GENERAL:
3269  {
3270  if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "func_invisible_user"))
3271  {
3272  // The damage flags tells us the type.
3273  switch (pEnt->s.dmgFlags)
3274  {
3275  case HINT_BUTTON:
3276  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_TRIGGER);
3277  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_STATIC);
3278  break;
3279  }
3280  }
3281  else if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "func_button"))
3282  {
3283  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_TRIGGER);
3284  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_STATIC);
3285  // continue for now so it doesnt get regged
3286  //continue;
3287  }
3288  else if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "misc_mg42"))
3289  {
3290  if ((pEnt->health > 0) &&
3291  (pEnt->entstate != STATE_INVISIBLE) &&
3292  (pEnt->entstate != STATE_UNDERCONSTRUCTION))
3293  {
3294  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_MOUNTEDWEAPON);
3295  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_SHOOTABLE);
3296  }
3297  }
3298  // cs: waypoint tool, don't merge the spawns
3299  else if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "info_player_deathmatch") ||
3300  !Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "team_CTF_redspawn") ||
3301  !Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "team_CTF_bluespawn") ||
3302  !Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "info_player_spawn"))
3303  {
3304  // don't fill up the bots sensory mem at start with these
3305  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_INTERNAL);
3306  }
3307  else
3308  {
3309  res = InvalidEntity;
3310  }
3311  break;
3312  }
3313  case ET_PLAYER:
3314  {
3315  if (!pEnt->client || (pEnt->entstate == STATE_INVISIBLE) ||
3316  (pEnt->client->ps.pm_type == PM_SPECTATOR) ||
3317  (pEnt->client->sess.sessionTeam != TEAM_AXIS &&
3318  pEnt->client->sess.sessionTeam != TEAM_ALLIES))
3319  {
3320  res = InvalidEntity;
3321  break;
3322  }
3323 
3324  // Special case for dead players that haven't respawned.
3325  if (pEnt->health <= GIB_HEALTH)
3326  {
3327  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_MISC);
3328  break;
3329  }
3330 
3331  if (pEnt->health > GIB_HEALTH)
3332  {
3333  if (!pEnt->client->ps.powerups[PW_INVULNERABLE])
3334  {
3335  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_SHOOTABLE);
3336  }
3337 
3338  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PLAYER);
3339  break;
3340  }
3341  }
3342  case ET_ITEM:
3343  {
3344  if (!(pEnt->r.contents & CONTENTS_ITEM))
3345  {
3346  res = InvalidEntity;
3347  }
3348  else if (!Q_strncmp(pEnt->classname, "item_health", 11))
3349  {
3350  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PICKUP);
3351  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PICKUP_HEALTH);
3352  }

3354  {
3355  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PICKUP);
3356  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PICKUP_AMMO);
3357  }
3358  else if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "item_treasure"))
3359  {
3360  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PICKUP);
3361  }
3362  else if (pEnt->item && pEnt->item->giType == IT_WEAPON)
3363  {
3364  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PICKUP);
3365  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PICKUP_WEAPON);
3366  }
3367  else
3368  {
3369  res = InvalidEntity;
3370  }
3371  break;
3372  }
3373  case ET_CORPSE:
3374  {
3375  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_MISC);
3376  break;
3377  }
3378  case ET_MISSILE:
3379  {

3384  case WP_GRENADE_PINEAPPLE:
3385  case WP_PANZERFAUST:
3386  case WP_ARTY:

3388  case WP_AIRSTRIKE:

3392  case WP_SATCHEL:
3393  case WP_M7:
3394  case WP_GPG40:
3395  case WP_MORTAR_SET:
3396 #if defined(NOQUARTER) || defined(LEGACY)
3397  case WP_MORTAR2_SET:
3398  case WP_BAZOOKA:
3399 #endif
3400  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_AVOID);
3401  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_PROJECTILE);
3402  break;
3403  case WP_LANDMINE:
3404 #ifdef JAYMOD_name
3405  case 79: //WP_LANDMINE_BBETTY
3406  case 80: //WP_LANDMINE_PGAS
3407 #endif
3408  _category.SetFlag(ENT_CAT_AVOID);
3409  _category.SetFlag(ET_ENT_CAT_MINE);

3566  obResult GetEntityFlags(const GameEntity _ent, BitFlag64 &_flags)
3567  {
3568  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
3569 
3570  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse)
3571  {
3572  // Set any flags.
3573  if (pEnt->health <= 0)
3574  {
3575  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DEAD);
3576  }
3577  if (pEnt->client && !IsBot(pEnt))
3578  {
3579  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_HUMANCONTROLLED);
3580  }
3581 
3582  if (pEnt->waterlevel >= 3)
3583  {
3584  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_UNDERWATER);
3585  }
3586  else if (pEnt->waterlevel > 0)
3587  {
3588  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_INWATER);
3589  }
3590 
3591  if (pEnt->s.eFlags & EF_ZOOMING)
3592  {
3593  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_ZOOMING);
3594  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_AIMING);
3595  }
3596 
3597  if (pEnt->s.eFlags & EF_MG42_ACTIVE)
3598  {
3599  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_MNT_MG42);
3600  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_MOUNTED);
3601  }
3602 
3603  if (pEnt->s.eFlags & EF_MOUNTEDTANK)
3604  {
3605  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_MNT_TANK);
3606  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_MOUNTED);
3607  }
3608 
3609 #ifndef NOQUARTER
3610  if (pEnt->s.eFlags & EF_AAGUN_ACTIVE)
3611  {
3612  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_MNT_AAGUN);
3613  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_MOUNTED);
3614  }
3615 #endif
3616 
3617  if (pEnt->s.eType == ET_HEALER || pEnt->s.eType == ET_SUPPLIER)
3618  {
3619  if (pEnt->entstate == STATE_INVISIBLE)
3620  {
3621  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DISABLED);
3622  }
3623  }
3624 
3625  if (pEnt->s.eType == ET_MOVER)
3626  {
3627  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_VISTEST);
3628  if (_TankIsMountable(pEnt))
3629  {
3630  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_ISMOUNTABLE);
3631  }
3632  if (G_TankIsOccupied(pEnt))
3633  {
3634  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_MOUNTED);
3635  }
3636  }
3637 
3638  if (pEnt->s.eType == ET_CONSTRUCTIBLE)
3639  {
3640  if (!G_ConstructionIsFullyBuilt(pEnt))
3641  {
3642  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DEAD);
3643  }
3644  else if (G_ConstructionIsFullyBuilt(pEnt))
3645  {
3646  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DEAD, false);
3647  }
3648  }
3649 
3650  if ((pEnt->s.eType == ET_MG42_BARREL) ||
3651  (pEnt->s.eType == ET_GENERAL && !Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "misc_mg42")))
3652  {
3653  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DEAD, Simple_EmplacedGunIsRepairable(pEnt) != 0);
3654 
3655  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_VISTEST);
3656  if (_EmplacedGunIsMountable(pEnt))
3657  {
3658  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_ISMOUNTABLE);
3659  }
3660 
3661  if (pEnt->r.ownerNum != pEnt->s.number)
3662  {
3663  gentity_t *owner = &g_entities[pEnt->r.ownerNum];
3664  if (owner && owner->active && owner->client && owner->s.eFlags & EF_MG42_ACTIVE)
3665  {
3666  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_MOUNTED);
3667  }
3668  }
3669  }
3670 
3671  if (pEnt->client)
3672  {
3673 #ifdef NOQUARTER
3674  if (pEnt->client->ps.eFlags & EF_POISONED)
3675  {
3676  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_POISONED);
3677  }
3678 #elif defined ETPUB_VERSION
3679  if (pEnt->client->pmext.poisoned)
3680  {
3681  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_POISONED);
3682  }
3683 #elif defined JAYMOD_name
3684  if (G_IsPoisoned(pEnt))
3685  {
3686  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_POISONED);
3687  }
3688 #endif
3689  if (pEnt->client->ps.pm_flags & PMF_LADDER)
3690  {
3691  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_ONLADDER);
3692  }
3693  if (pEnt->client->ps.eFlags & EF_PRONE)
3694  {
3695  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_PRONED);
3696  }
3697  if (pEnt->client->ps.pm_flags & PMF_DUCKED)
3698  {
3699  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_CROUCHED);
3700  }
3701  if (pEnt->client->ps.groundEntityNum != ENTITYNUM_NONE)
3702  {
3703  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_ONGROUND);
3704  }
3705  if (pEnt->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_RELOADING)
3706  {
3707  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_RELOADING);
3708  }
3709 
3710  if (pEnt->client->ps.powerups[PW_OPS_DISGUISED])
3711  {
3712  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_DISGUISED);
3713  }
3714  if (pEnt->client->ps.powerups[PW_REDFLAG] || pEnt->client->ps.powerups[PW_BLUEFLAG])
3715  {
3716  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_CARRYINGGOAL);
3717  }
3718  if (pEnt->client->ps.pm_flags & PMF_LIMBO)
3719  {
3720  _flags.SetFlag(ET_ENT_FLAG_INLIMBO);
3721  }
3722 
3723  switch (pEnt->client->ps.weapon)
3724  {
3725  case WP_GARAND_SCOPE:
3726  case WP_FG42SCOPE:
3727  case WP_K43_SCOPE:
3728  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_ZOOMING);
3729  break;
3730  }
3731  if (pEnt->s.eFlags & EF_ZOOMING)
3732  {
3733  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_ZOOMING);
3734  }
3735  }
3736 
3737  // hack, when the game joins clients again after warmup, they are temporarily ET_GENERAL entities(LAME)
3738  int t = pEnt->s.eType;
3739  if (pEnt->client && (pEnt - g_entities) < MAX_CLIENTS)
3740  {
3741  t = ET_PLAYER;
3742  }
3743 
3744  switch (t)
3745  {
3746  case ET_PLAYER:
3747  {
3748  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_VISTEST);
3749  if (pEnt->health <= 0)
3750  {
3751  if (!pEnt->r.linked || BODY_TEAM(pEnt) >= 4 || BODY_VALUE(pEnt) >= 250 || pEnt->health < GIB_HEALTH)
3752  {
3753  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DISABLED);
3754  }
3755  else if (g_OmniBotFlags.integer & OBF_GIBBING)
3756  {
3757  // for gibbing
3758  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DEAD, false);
3759  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_PRONED);
3760  }
3761  }
3762  break;
3763  }
3764  case ET_CORPSE:
3765  {
3766  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_VISTEST);
3767  if (!pEnt->r.linked || BODY_TEAM(pEnt) >= 4 || BODY_VALUE(pEnt) >= 250 || pEnt->health < GIB_HEALTH)
3768  {
3769  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DISABLED);
3770  }
3771  break;
3772  }
3773  case ET_ITEM:
3774  {
3775  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_VISTEST);
3776  if (!(pEnt->r.contents & CONTENTS_ITEM))
3777  {
3778  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DISABLED);
3779  }
3780  break;
3781  }
3782  case ET_HEALER:
3783  {
3784  break;
3785  }
3786  case ET_SUPPLIER:
3787  {
3788  break;
3789  }
3790  case ET_EXPLOSIVE:
3791  {
3792  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_VISTEST);
3793  break;
3794  }
3795  case ET_MISSILE:
3796  {
3797  // Register certain weapons as threats to avoid or whatever.
3798  switch (pEnt->s.weapon)
3799  {
3800  case WP_GRENADE_PINEAPPLE:
3801  case WP_GRENADE_LAUNCHER:
3802  case WP_PANZERFAUST:
3803  case WP_ARTY:
3804 #if defined(LEGACY)
3805  case WP_AIRSTRIKE:
3806 #endif
3807  case WP_DYNAMITE:
3808  case WP_SMOKE_MARKER:
3809  case WP_LANDMINE:
3810  case WP_SATCHEL:
3811  case WP_M7:
3812  case WP_GPG40:
3813  case WP_MORTAR_SET:
3814 #if defined(NOQUARTER) || defined(LEGACY)
3815  case WP_MORTAR2_SET:
3816  case WP_BAZOOKA:
3817 #endif
3818  case WP_SMOKE_BOMB:
3819  // FIXME: fallthrough ??
3820  default:
3821  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_VISTEST);
3822  }
3823  break;
3824  }
3825  case ET_GENERAL:
3826  case ET_MG42_BARREL:
3827  {
3828  if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "misc_mg42"))
3829  {
3830  if ((pEnt->health < 0) ||
3831  (pEnt->entstate == STATE_INVISIBLE))
3832  {
3833  //_flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_VISTEST);
3834  _flags.SetFlag(ENT_FLAG_DEAD);
3835  }
3836  }
3837  break;
3838  }
3839  }
3840  }
3841  return Success;
3842  }

3869  obResult GetEntityOrientation(const GameEntity _ent, float _fwd[3], float _right[3], float _up[3])

3887  obResult GetEntityVelocity(const GameEntity _ent, float _velocity[3])
3888  {
3889  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
3890  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse)
3891  {
3892  // hack, when the game joins clients again after warmup, they are temporarily ET_GENERAL entities(LAME)
3893  int t = pEnt->s.eType;
3894  if (pEnt->client && (pEnt - g_entities) < MAX_CLIENTS)
3895  {
3896  t = ET_PLAYER;
3897  }
3898 
3899  if (t == ET_MOVER)
3900  {
3901  // Calculate the velocity ourselves. for some reason mover velocity
3902  // isn't in s.pos.trDelta
3903  const float fDeltaTime = 50.0f; // get this dynamically?
3904  _velocity[0] = (pEnt->r.currentOrigin[0] - pEnt->oldOrigin[0]) * fDeltaTime;
3905  _velocity[1] = (pEnt->r.currentOrigin[1] - pEnt->oldOrigin[1]) * fDeltaTime;
3906  _velocity[2] = (pEnt->r.currentOrigin[2] - pEnt->oldOrigin[2]) * fDeltaTime;
3907  }
3908  else
3909  {
3910  _velocity[0] = pEnt->s.pos.trDelta[0];
3911  _velocity[1] = pEnt->s.pos.trDelta[1];
3912  _velocity[2] = pEnt->s.pos.trDelta[2];
3913  }
3914  return Success;
3915  }
3916  return InvalidEntity;
3917  }
3918 
3919  obResult GetEntityPosition(const GameEntity _ent, float _pos[3])
3920  {
3921  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
3922  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse)
3923  {
3924  if (!pEnt->client)
3925  {
3926  vec3_t axis[3];
3927  //AngleVectors( pEnt->r.currentAngles, axis[0], axis[1], axis[2] );
3928  AnglesToAxis(pEnt->r.currentAngles, axis);
3929 
3930  vec3_t boxCenter;
3931  boxCenter[0] = ((pEnt->r.maxs[0] + pEnt->r.mins[0]) * 0.5f);
3932  boxCenter[1] = ((pEnt->r.maxs[1] + pEnt->r.mins[1]) * 0.5f);
3933  boxCenter[2] = ((pEnt->r.maxs[2] + pEnt->r.mins[2]) * 0.5f);
3934 
3935  vec3_t out;
3936  VectorCopy(pEnt->r.currentOrigin, out);
3937  for (int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
3938  {
3939  vec3_t tmp;
3940  VectorScale(axis[i], boxCenter[i], tmp);
3941  VectorAdd(out, tmp, out);
3942  }
3943  VectorCopy(out, _pos);
3944  return Success;
3945  }
3946  else if (!g_dedicated.integer && _ent.GetIndex() == 0 && pEnt->client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_SPECTATOR)
3947  {
3948  //local spectator
3949  _pos[0] = pEnt->client->ps.origin[0];
3950  _pos[1] = pEnt->client->ps.origin[1];
3951  _pos[2] = pEnt->client->ps.origin[2];
3952  }
3953  else
3954  {
3955 
3956  // Clients return normal position.
3957  _pos[0] = pEnt->r.currentOrigin[0];
3958  _pos[1] = pEnt->r.currentOrigin[1];
3959  _pos[2] = pEnt->r.currentOrigin[2];
3960  }
3961 
3962  return Success;
3963  }
3964  return InvalidEntity;
3965  }

4061  obResult GetEntityWorldAABB(const GameEntity _ent, AABB &_aabb)
4062  {
4063  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
4064  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse)
4065  {
4066  /*if(!pEnt->r.linked && pEnt->parent && pEnt->parent->s.eType == ET_OID_TRIGGER)
4067  pEnt = pEnt->parent;*/
4068 
4069  if (pEnt->s.eType == ET_CONSTRUCTIBLE)
4070  {
4071  gentity_t *pAxis = G_ConstructionForTeam(pEnt->parent ? pEnt->parent : pEnt, TEAM_AXIS);
4072  gentity_t *pAlly = G_ConstructionForTeam(pEnt->parent ? pEnt->parent : pEnt, TEAM_ALLIES);
4073  if (pAxis /*&& pAxis->entstate == STATE_DEFAULT*/)
4074  {
4075  pEnt = pAxis;
4076  }
4077  else if (pAlly /*&& pAlly->entstate == STATE_DEFAULT*/)
4078  {
4079  pEnt = pAlly;
4080  }
4081  }
4082 
4083  if (!g_dedicated.integer && _ent.GetIndex() == 0 && pEnt->client && pEnt->client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_SPECTATOR)
4084  {
4085  //local spectator
4086  playerState_t *ps = &pEnt->client->ps;
4087  for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++)
4088  {
4089  _aabb.m_Mins[i] = ps->origin[i] + ps->mins[i] - 1;
4090  _aabb.m_Maxs[i] = ps->origin[i] + ps->maxs[i] + 1;
4091  }
4092  }
4093  else
4094  {
4095  _aabb.m_Mins[0] = pEnt->r.absmin[0];
4096  _aabb.m_Mins[1] = pEnt->r.absmin[1];
4097  _aabb.m_Mins[2] = pEnt->r.absmin[2];
4098  _aabb.m_Maxs[0] = pEnt->r.absmax[0];
4099  _aabb.m_Maxs[1] = pEnt->r.absmax[1];
4100  _aabb.m_Maxs[2] = pEnt->r.absmax[2];
4101  }
4102 
4103  // raise player bounds slightly since it appears to be in the ground a bit
4104  if (pEnt->client)
4105  {
4106  _aabb.m_Mins[2] += 2.f;
4107  _aabb.m_Maxs[2] += 2.f;
4108  }
4109 
4110  // hack for bad abs bounds
4111  if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "misc_mg42"))
4112  {
4113  if (_aabb.IsZero() || !_aabb.Contains(pEnt->r.currentOrigin))
4114  {
4115  float pos[3] = { 0, 0, 0 };
4116  const float default_box_mins[] = { -8, -8, -8 };
4117  const float default_box_maxs[] = { 8, 8, 48 };
4118  GetEntityPosition(_ent, pos);
4119  _aabb.Set(default_box_mins, default_box_maxs);
4120  _aabb.SetCenter(pos);
4121  }
4122  }
4123  return Success;
4124  }
4125  return InvalidEntity;
4126  }
4127 
4128  obResult GetEntityWorldOBB(const GameEntity _ent, float *_center, float *_axis0, float *_axis1, float *_axis2, float *_extents)
4129  {
4130  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
4131  if (pEnt)
4132  {
4133  vec3_t axis[3];
4134  AnglesToAxis(pEnt->r.currentAngles, axis);
4135 
4136  vec3_t boxCenter;
4137  boxCenter[0] = ((pEnt->r.maxs[0] + pEnt->r.mins[0]) * 0.5f);
4138  boxCenter[1] = ((pEnt->r.maxs[1] + pEnt->r.mins[1]) * 0.5f);
4139  boxCenter[2] = ((pEnt->r.maxs[2] + pEnt->r.mins[2]) * 0.5f);
4140 
4141  vec3_t out;
4142  VectorCopy(pEnt->r.currentOrigin, out);
4143  for (int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4144  {
4145  vec3_t tmp;
4146  VectorScale(axis[i], boxCenter[i], tmp);
4147  VectorAdd(out, tmp, out);
4148  }
4149  VectorCopy(out, _center);
4150  VectorCopy(axis[0], _axis0);
4151  VectorCopy(axis[1], _axis1);
4152  VectorCopy(axis[2], _axis2);
4153  _extents[0] = (pEnt->r.maxs[0] - pEnt->r.mins[0]) * 0.5f;
4154  _extents[1] = (pEnt->r.maxs[1] - pEnt->r.mins[1]) * 0.5f;
4155  _extents[2] = (pEnt->r.maxs[2] - pEnt->r.mins[2]) * 0.5f;
4156 
4157  return Success;
4158  }
4159  return InvalidEntity;
4160  }

4176  GameEntity GetEntityOwner(const GameEntity _ent)
4177  {
4178  GameEntity owner;
4179 
4180  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
4181  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse)
4182  {
4183  // hack, when the game joins clients again after warmup, they are temporarily ET_GENERAL entities(LAME)
4184  int t = pEnt->s.eType;
4185  if (pEnt->client && (pEnt - g_entities) < MAX_CLIENTS)
4186  {
4187  t = ET_PLAYER;
4188  }
4189 
4190  switch (t)
4191  {
4192  case ET_ITEM:
4193  {
4194  if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "team_CTF_redflag") ||
4195  !Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "team_CTF_blueflag"))
4196  {
4197  int iFlagEntNum = pEnt - g_entities;
4198  for (int i = 0; i < g_maxclients.integer; ++i)
4199  {
4200  if (g_entities[i].inuse && g_entities[i].client && g_entities[i].client->flagParent == iFlagEntNum)
4201  {
4202  owner = HandleFromEntity(&g_entities[i]);
4203  }
4204  }
4205  }
4206  break;
4207  }
4208  case ET_GENERAL:
4209  case ET_MG42_BARREL:
4210  {
4211  if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "misc_mg42"))
4212  {
4213  if (pEnt->r.ownerNum != pEnt->s.number)
4214  {
4215  gentity_t *pOwner = &g_entities[pEnt->r.ownerNum];
4216  if (pOwner && pOwner->active && pOwner->client && (pOwner->s.eFlags & EF_MG42_ACTIVE))
4217  {
4218  owner = HandleFromEntity(pOwner);
4219  }
4220  }
4221  }
4222  break;
4223  }
4224  default:
4225  // -1 means theres no owner.
4226  if (pEnt->r.ownerNum < MAX_GENTITIES)
4227  {
4228  owner = HandleFromEntity(&g_entities[pEnt->r.ownerNum]);
4229  }
4230  }
4231  }
4232  return owner;
4233  }

4831  void GetPlayerInfo(obPlayerInfo &info)
4832  {
4833  info.m_AvailableTeams |= (1 << ET_TEAM_ALLIES);
4834  info.m_AvailableTeams |= (1 << ET_TEAM_AXIS);
4835 
4836  info.m_MaxPlayers = level.maxclients;
4837 
4838 
4839  GameEntity ge;
4840 
4841  for (int i = 0; i < g_maxclients.integer; ++i)
4842  {
4843  if (!g_entities[i].inuse)
4844  {
4845  continue;
4846  }
4847  if (!g_entities[i].client)
4848  {
4849  continue;
4850  }
4851  if (g_entities[i].client->pers.connected != CON_CONNECTED)
4852  {
4853  continue;
4854  }
4855 
4856  ge = HandleFromEntity(&g_entities[i]);
4857 
4858  info.m_Players[i].m_Team = GetEntityTeam(ge);
4859  info.m_Players[i].m_Class = GetEntityClass(ge);
4860  info.m_Players[i].m_Controller = IsBot(&g_entities[i]) ?
4861  obPlayerInfo::Bot : obPlayerInfo::Human;
4862  }
4863  }

4865  obResult InterfaceSendMessage(const MessageHelper &_data, const GameEntity _ent)
4866  {
4867  gentity_t *pEnt = EntityFromHandle(_ent);
4868 
4869  switch (_data.GetMessageId())
4870  {
4871  // general messages
4872  case GEN_MSG_ISALIVE:
4873  {
4874  OB_GETMSG(Msg_IsAlive);
4875  if (pMsg)
4876  {
4877  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse && pEnt->client && pEnt->health > 0 &&
4878  pEnt->client->ps.pm_type == PM_NORMAL)
4879  {
4880  pMsg->m_IsAlive = True;
4881  }
4882  }
4883  break;
4884  }
4885  case GEN_MSG_ISRELOADING:
4886  {
4887  OB_GETMSG(Msg_Reloading);
4888  if (pMsg)
4889  {
4890  if ((pEnt && pEnt->inuse && pEnt->client && pEnt->client->ps.weaponstate >= WEAPON_RAISING) &&
4891  (pEnt->client->ps.weaponstate <= WEAPON_RELOADING))
4892  {
4893  pMsg->m_Reloading = True;
4894  }
4895  }
4896  break;
4897  }
4898  case GEN_MSG_ISREADYTOFIRE:
4899  {
4900  OB_GETMSG(Msg_ReadyToFire);
4901  if (pMsg)
4902  {
4903  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse && pEnt->client)
4904  {
4905  if (pEnt->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_READY || pEnt->client->ps.weaponstate == WEAPON_FIRING)
4906  {
4907  pMsg->m_Ready = True;
4908  }
4909  }
4910  }
4911  break;
4912  }
4913  case GEN_MSG_GETEQUIPPEDWEAPON:
4914  {
4915  OB_GETMSG(WeaponStatus);
4916  if (pMsg)
4917  {
4918  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse && pEnt->client)
4919  {
4920  pMsg->m_WeaponId = Bot_WeaponGameToBot(pEnt->client->ps.weapon);
4921  }
4922  else
4923  {
4924  pMsg->m_WeaponId = 0;
4925  }
4926  }
4927  break;
4928  }
4929  case GEN_MSG_GETMOUNTEDWEAPON:
4930  {
4931  OB_GETMSG(WeaponStatus);
4932  if (pMsg && pEnt && pEnt->inuse && pEnt->client)
4933  {
4934  pMsg->m_WeaponId = BG_PlayerMounted(pEnt->s.eFlags) ? ET_WP_MOUNTABLE_MG42 : ET_WP_NONE;
4935  }
4936  break;
4937  }
4938  case GEN_MSG_GETWEAPONLIMITS:
4939  {
4940  OB_GETMSG(WeaponLimits);
4941  if (pMsg)
4942  {
4943 
4944  if (pEnt && pEnt->inuse && pEnt->client)
4945  {
4946  if (pMsg->m_WeaponId == ET_WP_MOUNTABLE_MG42 &&
4947  BG_PlayerMounted(pEnt->client->ps.eFlags))
4948  {
4949  pMsg->m_Limited = True;
4950  AngleVectors(pEnt->client->pmext.centerangles, pMsg->m_CenterFacing, NULL, NULL);
4951  if (pEnt->client->ps.eFlags & EF_MOUNTEDTANK)
4952  {
4953  // seems tanks have complete horizonal movement, and fixed vertical
4954  pMsg->m_MinYaw = -360;
4955  pMsg->m_MaxYaw = -360;
4956  pMsg->m_MinPitch = 14;
4957  pMsg->m_MaxPitch = 50;
4958  }
4959  else
4960  {
4961  pMsg->m_MinYaw = -pEnt->client->pmext.harc;
4962  pMsg->m_MaxYaw = pEnt->client->pmext.harc;
4963  pMsg->m_MinPitch = -pEnt->client->pmext.varc;
4964  pMsg->m_MaxPitch = pEnt->client->pmext.varc;
4965  }
4966  }
4967  if (pMsg->m_WeaponId == ET_WP_MOBILE_MG42 || pMsg->m_WeaponId == ET_WP_MOBILE_MG42_SET)
4968  {
4969  AngleVectors(pEnt->client->pmext.mountedWeaponAngles, pMsg->m_CenterFacing, NULL, NULL);
4970  pMsg->m_Limited = True;
4971  pMsg->m_MinYaw = -20.f;
4972  pMsg->m_MaxYaw = 20.f;
4973  pMsg->m_MinPitch = -20.f;
4974  pMsg->m_MaxPitch = 20.f;
4975  }
4976  }
4977  else
4978  {
4979  pMsg->m_Limited = False;
4980  }
4981  }
4983  break;
4984  }
4985  case GEN_MSG_GETHEALTHARMOR:
4986  {
4987  OB_GETMSG(Msg_HealthArmor);
4988  if (pMsg)
4989  {
4990  // No Armor in ET
4991  pMsg->m_CurrentArmor = pMsg->m_MaxArmor = 0;
4992  if (pEnt)
4993  {
4994  switch (pEnt->s.eType)
4995  {
4996  case ET_MOVER:
4997  case ET_CONSTRUCTIBLE:
4998  pMsg->m_CurrentHealth = pEnt->takedamage ? pEnt->health > 0 ? pEnt->health : 0 : 0;
4999  pMsg->m_MaxHealth = pEnt->count;
5000  break;
5001  case ET_GENERAL:
5002  case ET_MG42_BARREL:
5003  if (!Q_stricmp(pEnt->classname, "misc_mg42"))
5004  {
5005  if (Simple_EmplacedGunIsRepairable(pEnt))
5006  {
5007  pMsg->m_CurrentHealth = 0;
5008  pMsg->m_MaxHealth = MG42_MULTIPLAYER_HEALTH;

5016  pMsg->m_MaxHealth = MG42_MULTIPLAYER_HEALTH;
5017  }
5018  else
5019  {
5020  // just in case
5021  pMsg->m_CurrentHealth = pEnt->health;
5022  pMsg->m_MaxHealth = MG42_MULTIPLAYER_HEALTH;
5023  }
5024  }
5025  }
5026  break;
5027  default:
5028  if (pEnt->client)
5029  {
5030  pMsg->m_CurrentHealth = pEnt->client->ps.stats[STAT_HEALTH];
5031  pMsg->m_MaxHealth = pEnt->client->ps.stats[STAT_MAX_HEALTH];
5032  }
5033  else

5035  pMsg->m_CurrentHealth = pEnt->takedamage ? pEnt->health : 0;
5036  pMsg->m_MaxHealth = 0;
5037  }
5038  }
5039  }
5040  }
5041  break;
5042  }
5043  case GEN_MSG_GETMAXSPEED:

5046  if (pMsg && pEnt)
5047  {
5048  pMsg->m_MaxSpeed = (float)g_movespeed.integer;
5049  }
5050  break;
5051  }
5052  case GEN_MSG_ISALLIED:
5053  {

5055  if (pMsg)

5057  gentity_t *pEntOther = EntityFromHandle(pMsg->m_TargetEntity);
5058  if (pEntOther && pEnt)
5059  {
5060  if (ENTINDEX(pEntOther) == ENTITYNUM_WORLD)
5061  {
5062  pMsg->m_IsAllied = True;
5063  }
5064  else
5065  {
5066  pMsg->m_IsAllied = _GetEntityTeam(pEnt) == _GetEntityTeam(pEntOther) ? True : False;
5067  }
5068  }
5069  }
5070  break;
5071  }

5073  {
5074  OB_GETMSG(Msg_IsOutside);
5075  if (pMsg)
5076  {
5077  trace_t tr;
5078  vec3_t end = { pMsg->m_Position[0], pMsg->m_Position[1], (pMsg->m_Position[2] + 4096) };
5079  trap_Trace(&tr, pMsg->m_Position, NULL, NULL, end, -1, MASK_SOLID);
5080

5082  {

5084  }
5085  else

5088  }
5089  }

5101  ClientUserinfoChanged(pEnt - g_entities);
5102  }
5103  break;
5104  }
5105  case GEN_MSG_ENTITYKILL:
5106  {
5107  OB_GETMSG(Msg_KillEntity);

5110  gentity_t *pWho = EntityFromHandle(pMsg->m_WhoToKill);
5111  if (pWho)
5112  {
5113  G_Damage(pWho, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, pWho->client ? GIB_DAMAGE(pWho->health) : GIB_ENT, DAMAGE_NO_PROTECTION, MOD_TELEFRAG);

5116  break;
5117  }

5124  }
5125  break;
5126  }
5127  case GEN_MSG_GETFLAGSTATE:
5128  {
5129  OB_GETMSG(Msg_FlagState);
5130  if (pMsg)

5132  /* CS: flagreturn position is not updated while its carried.

5145  }

5767  OB_GETMSG(ET_CanBeGrabbed);
5768  if (pMsg)
5769  {
5770  //CS: testing flagstate
5771  //pMsg->m_CanBeGrabbed = True;
5772 
5773 
5774  gentity_t *pFlagEnt = EntityFromHandle(pMsg->m_Entity);
5775  if (pEnt && pEnt->client && pFlagEnt)
5776  {
5777  // DUPLICATE ERROR CHECK, so BG_CanItemBeGrabbed doesn't screw up.
5778  if (pFlagEnt->s.modelindex < 1 || pFlagEnt->s.modelindex >= ITEM_MAX_ITEMS)
5779  {
5780  //Com_Error( ERR_DROP, "BG_CanItemBeGrabbed: index out of range" );
5781  pMsg->m_CanBeGrabbed = Invalid;
5782  }
5783  else
5784  {
5785  pMsg->m_CanBeGrabbed =
5786  BG_CanItemBeGrabbed(&pFlagEnt->s, &pEnt->client->ps,
5787  pEnt->client->sess.skill, pEnt->client->sess.sessionTeam) ? True : False;
5788 
5789  // When flags aren't dropped, we need to reject some pickup cases
5790  // This is because the return flag goal uses this function to see if they can
5791  // grab/return a flag
5792  if (pMsg->m_CanBeGrabbed == True && !(pFlagEnt->flags & FL_DROPPED_ITEM))
5793  {
5794  if ((pEnt->client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_AXIS) &&
5795  !Q_stricmp(pFlagEnt->classname, "team_CTF_redflag"))
5796  {
5797  GameEntity owner = GetEntityOwner(pMsg->m_Entity);
5798  if (!owner.IsValid())
5799  {
5800  pMsg->m_CanBeGrabbed = False;
5801  }
5802  }
5803  else if ((pEnt->client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_ALLIES) &&
5804  !Q_stricmp(pFlagEnt->classname, "team_CTF_blueflag"))
5805  {
5806  GameEntity owner = GetEntityOwner(pMsg->m_Entity);
5807  if (!owner.IsValid())
5808  {
5809  pMsg->m_CanBeGrabbed = False;
5810  }
5811  }
5812  }
5813  }
5814 
5815  }
5816  }
5817  break;
5818  }
5819  case ET_MSG_GNUMTEAMMINES:
5820  {
5821  OB_GETMSG(ET_TeamMines);
5822  if (pMsg)
5823  {
5824  if (pEnt && pEnt->client)
5825  {
5826  pMsg->m_Current = G_CountTeamLandmines(pEnt->client->sess.sessionTeam);
5827 #if defined(NOQUARTER) || defined(LEGACY)
5828  pMsg->m_Max = team_maxLandmines.integer;
5829 #elif defined ETPUB_VERSION
5830  pMsg->m_Max = g_maxTeamLandmines.integer;
5831 #else
5832  pMsg->m_Max = MAX_TEAM_LANDMINES;
5833 #endif
5834  }
5835  }
5836  break;
5837  }
5838  case ET_MSG_CABINETDATA:
5839  {
5840  OB_GETMSG(ET_CabinetData);
5841  if (pMsg)
5842  {
5843  if (pEnt && (pEnt->s.eType == ET_HEALER || pEnt->s.eType == ET_SUPPLIER))
5844  {
5845  pMsg->m_Rate = pEnt->damage;
5846  pMsg->m_CurrentAmount = pEnt->health;
5847  pMsg->m_MaxAmount = pEnt->count;
5848  }
5849  else
5850  {
5851  return InvalidEntity;
5852  }
5853  }
5854  break;
5855  }
5856  case ET_MSG_SKILLLEVEL:

5860  OB_GETMSG(ET_PlayerSkills);

5862  pMsg->m_Skill[ET_SKILL_ENGINEERING] = pEnt->client->sess.skill[SK_EXPLOSIVES_AND_CONSTRUCTION];

5970  pMsg->m_InFireTeam = True;

6007  case ET_MSG_GETCVAR:
6008  {
6009  OB_GETMSG(ET_CvarGet);
6010  if (pMsg)
6011  {
6012  pMsg->m_Value =
6013  trap_Cvar_VariableIntegerValue(pMsg->m_Cvar);
6014  }
6015  break;
6016  }

6018  {
6019  OB_GETMSG(ET_DisableBotPush);
6020  if (pMsg)
6021  {
6022  if (pEnt && pEnt->client)
6023  {
6024  if (pMsg->m_Push > 0)
6025  {
6026  pEnt->client->sess.botPush = qfalse;
6027  }
6028  else
6029  {
6030  pEnt->client->sess.botPush = qtrue;
6031  }
6032  }
6033  }
6034  break;
6035  }
6036  default:
6037  {
6038  return UnknownMessageType;
6039  }
6040  }
6041  return Success;
6042  }

6052  void PrintMessage(const char *_msg)
6053  {
6054  if (_msg)
6055  {
6056  // et console doesn't support tabs, so
6057  const int BufferSize = 1024;
6058  char tmpbuffer[BufferSize];
6059  const char *src = _msg;
6060  char *dest = tmpbuffer;
6061  while (*src != 0 && dest < tmpbuffer + BufferSize - 4)
6062  {
6063  if (*src == '\t')
6064  {
6065  for (int i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
6066  *dest++ = ' ';
6067  }
6068  else
6069  {
6070  *dest++ = *src;
6071  }
6072  src++;
6073  }
6074  *dest = 0;
6075  G_Printf("%s%s\n", S_COLOR_GREEN, tmpbuffer);
6076  }
6077  }

6115  void GetMapExtents(AABB &_aabb)
6116  {
6117  if (level.mapcoordsValid)
6118  {
6119  _aabb.m_Mins[0] = level.mapcoordsMins[0] ;
6120  _aabb.m_Mins[1] = level.mapcoordsMins[1] ;
6121  _aabb.m_Mins[2] = -65535.0f;
6122  _aabb.m_Maxs[0] = level.mapcoordsMaxs[0] ;
6123  _aabb.m_Maxs[1] = level.mapcoordsMaxs[1] ;
6124  _aabb.m_Maxs[2] = 65535.0f;
6125 
6126  for (int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6127  {
6128  if (_aabb.m_Mins[i] > _aabb.m_Maxs[i])
6129  {
6130  float t = _aabb.m_Mins[i];
6131  _aabb.m_Mins[i] = _aabb.m_Maxs[i];
6132  _aabb.m_Maxs[i] = t;
6133  }
6134  }
6135  }
6136  else
6137  {
6138  Com_Memset(&_aabb, 0, sizeof(AABB));
6139  }
6140  }

6154  int IDFromEntity(const GameEntity _ent)

6160  int iIndex = pEnt - pStart;

6163  }
6164  return -1;

6172  int GetAutoNavFeatures(AutoNavFeature *_feature, int _max)
6173  {
6174  int iNumFeatures = 0;
6175  for (int i = MAX_CLIENTS; i < level.num_entities; ++i)
6176  {
6177  gentity_t *e = &g_entities[i];
6178 
6179  if (!e->inuse)
6180  {
6181  continue;
6182  }
6183 
6185  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = 0;
6186  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_TravelTime = 0;
6187  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_ObstacleEntity = false;
6188  for (int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6189  {
6190  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Position[i] = e->r.currentOrigin[i];
6191  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_TargetPosition[i] = e->r.currentOrigin[i];
6192  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Bounds.m_Mins[0] = 0.f;
6193  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Bounds.m_Maxs[0] = 0.f;
6194  AngleVectors(e->s.angles, _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Facing, NULL, NULL);
6195  }
6196 
6197  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Bounds.m_Mins[0] = e->r.absmin[0];
6198  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Bounds.m_Mins[1] = e->r.absmin[1];
6199  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Bounds.m_Mins[2] = e->r.absmin[2];
6200  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Bounds.m_Maxs[0] = e->r.absmax[0];
6201  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Bounds.m_Maxs[1] = e->r.absmax[1];
6202  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Bounds.m_Maxs[2] = e->r.absmax[2];
6204  if (e->classname)
6205  {
6206  if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "team_CTF_redspawn"))
6207  {
6208  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_PLAYERSTART_TEAM1;
6209  }
6210  else if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "team_CTF_bluespawn"))
6211  {
6212  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_PLAYERSTART_TEAM2;
6213  }
6214  else if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "info_player_deathmatch") ||
6215  !Q_stricmp(e->classname, "info_player_spawn"))
6216  {
6217  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_PLAYERSTART;
6218  }
6219  else if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "target_teleporter"))
6220  {
6221  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_TELEPORTER;
6222  gentity_t *pTarget = G_PickTarget(e->target);
6223  if (pTarget)
6224  {
6225  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_TargetPosition[0] = pTarget->r.currentOrigin[0];
6226  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_TargetPosition[1] = pTarget->r.currentOrigin[1];
6227  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_TargetPosition[2] = pTarget->r.currentOrigin[2];
6228  }
6229  }
6230  else if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "team_CTF_redflag"))
6231  {
6232  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_FLAG;
6233  }
6234  else if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "team_CTF_blueflag"))
6235  {
6236  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ENT_CLASS_GENERIC_FLAG;
6237  }
6238  else if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "misc_mg42") || !Q_stricmp(e->classname, "misc_mg42base"))
6239  {
6240  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ET_CLASSEX_MG42MOUNT;
6241  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_ObstacleEntity = true;
6242  }
6243  else if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "misc_cabinet_health"))
6244  {
6245  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ET_CLASSEX_HEALTHCABINET;
6246  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_ObstacleEntity = true;
6247  }
6248  else if (!Q_stricmp(e->classname, "misc_cabinet_supply"))
6249  {
6250  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type = ET_CLASSEX_AMMOCABINET;
6251  _feature[iNumFeatures].m_ObstacleEntity = true;
6252  }
6253  }
6254 
6255  if (_feature[iNumFeatures].m_Type != 0)
6256  {
6257  iNumFeatures++;
6258  }
6259  }
6260  return iNumFeatures;
6261  }

6301 int Bot_Interface_Init()
6302 {
6303  g_GoalSubmitReady = false;
6304 
6305  if (g_OmniBotEnable.integer == 0)
6306  {
6307  G_Printf("%s%s\n", S_COLOR_GREEN,
6308  "Omni-bot is currently disabled with \"omnibot_enable 0\"");
6309  return 1;
6310  }
6311 
6312 #if defined(_DEBUG) || defined(LEGACY_DEBUG)
6313  trap_Cvar_Set("sv_cheats", "1");
6314  trap_Cvar_Update(&g_cheats);
6315 #endif
6316 
6317  g_InterfaceFunctions = new ETInterface;
6318  eomnibot_error err = Omnibot_LoadLibrary(ET_VERSION_LATEST,
6319  "omnibot_et", Omnibot_FixPath(g_OmniBotPath.string));
6320  if (err == BOT_ERROR_NONE)
6321  {
6322  return true;
6323  }
6324  return false;
6325 }

6332  }
6333  Omnibot_FreeLibrary();
6334  return 1;

6339 void Bot_Interface_ConsoleCommand(void)
6340 {
6341  enum { BuffSize=32 };
6342  char buffer[BuffSize] = {};
6343  trap_Argv(1, buffer, BuffSize);
6344 
6345  if (IsOmnibotLoaded())
6346  {
6347  if (!Q_stricmp(buffer, "unload"))
6348  {
6349  Bot_Interface_Shutdown();
6350  return;
6351  }
6352  else if (!Q_stricmp(buffer, "reload"))
6353  {
6354  Bot_Interface_Shutdown();
6355  Bot_Interface_InitHandles();
6356  Bot_Interface_Init();
6357  return;
6358  }
6359 
6360  Arguments args;
6361  for (int i = 0; i < trap_Argc(); ++i)
6362  {
6363  trap_Argv(i, args.m_Args[args.m_NumArgs++], Arguments::MaxArgLength);
6364  }
6365  g_BotFunctions.pfnConsoleCommand(args);
6366  }
6367  else
6368  {
6369  if (!Q_stricmp(buffer, "load"))
6370  {
6371  Bot_Interface_InitHandles();
6372  Bot_Interface_Init();
6373  return;
6374  }
6375  else
6376  {
6377  G_Printf("%s%s\n", S_COLOR_RED, "Omni-bot not loaded.");
6378  }
6379  }
6380 
6381 }

6383 extern "C" void script_mover_spawn(gentity_t *ent);
6384 void Bot_Interface_Update()
6385 {
6386  if (IsOmnibotLoaded())
6387  {
6388  char buf[1024] = { 0 };
6389 
6390 //#if defined(_DEBUG) || defined(LEGACY_DEBUG)
6391 // trap_Cvar_Set( "sv_cheats", "1" );
6392 // trap_Cvar_Update(&g_cheats);
6393 //#endif
6394  /*if (level.framenum == GAME_INIT_FRAMES)
6395  Bot_Event_StartGame();*/
6396 
6398  {
6399  // time triggers for Omni-bot
6400 #if defined(NOQUARTER) || defined(LEGACY)
6401  if (level.framenum % sv_fps.integer == 0)
6402 #else
6403  if (level.framenum % 20 == 0) //@sv_fps
6404 #endif
6405  {
6406  if (!level.twoMinute && (g_timelimit.value * 60000 - (level.time - level.startTime)) < 120000)
6407  {
6408  level.twoMinute = qtrue;
6409  Bot_Util_SendTrigger(NULL, NULL, "two minute warning.", "twominute");
6410  }
6411 
6412  if (!level.thirtySecond && (g_timelimit.value * 60000 - (level.time - level.startTime)) < 30000)
6413  {
6414  level.thirtySecond = qtrue;
6415  Bot_Util_SendTrigger(NULL, NULL, "thirty second warning.", "thirtysecond");
6416  }
6417  }
6418  }
6420  {
6421  static float serverGravity = 0.0f;
6422  if (serverGravity != g_gravity.value)
6423  {
6424  Event_SystemGravity d = { -g_gravity.value };
6425  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendGlobalEvent(MessageHelper(GAME_GRAVITY, &d, sizeof(d)));
6426  serverGravity = g_gravity.value;
6427  }
6428  static int cheatsEnabled = 0;
6429  if (g_cheats.integer != cheatsEnabled)
6430  {
6431  Event_SystemCheats d = { g_cheats.integer ? True : False };
6432  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendGlobalEvent(MessageHelper(GAME_CHEATS, &d, sizeof(d)));
6433  cheatsEnabled = g_cheats.integer;
6434  }
6435  }
6436 
6437  int iNumBots = 0;
6438  for (int i = 0; i < g_maxclients.integer; ++i)
6439  {
6440  if (!g_entities[i].inuse)
6441  {
6442  continue;
6443  }
6444  if (!g_entities[i].client)
6445  {
6446  continue;
6447  }
6448  if (g_entities[i].client->pers.connected != CON_CONNECTED)
6449  {
6450  continue;
6451  }
6452 
6453  /*if(i==1)
6454  g_entities[i].flags |= FL_GODMODE;*/
6455 
6456  // Send a spectated message to bots that are being spectated.
6457  if ((g_entities[i].client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_SPECTATOR) &&
6458  (g_entities[i].client->sess.spectatorState == SPECTATOR_FOLLOW))
6459  {
6460  int iDestination = g_entities[i].client->sess.spectatorClient;
6461  Bot_Event_Spectated(iDestination, i);
6462  }
6463 
6464  // fake handle server commands (to prevent server command overflow)
6465  if ((g_entities[i].inuse == qtrue) && IsBot(&g_entities[i]))
6466  {
6467  ++iNumBots;
6468  while (trap_BotGetServerCommand(i, buf, sizeof(buf)))
6469  {
6470  }
6471  }
6472  }
6473 
6474  if (!(g_OmniBotFlags.integer & OBF_DONT_SHOW_BOTCOUNT))
6475  {
6476  if (g_OmniBotPlaying.integer != iNumBots)
6477  {
6478  g_OmniBotPlaying.integer = iNumBots;
6479  trap_Cvar_Set("omnibot_playing", va("%i", iNumBots));
6480  }
6481  }
6482  else
6483  {
6484  if (g_OmniBotPlaying.integer != -1)
6485  {
6486  g_OmniBotPlaying.integer = -1;
6487  trap_Cvar_Set("omnibot_playing", "-1");
6488  }
6489  }
6490 
6492  // Register any pending entity updates.
6493  for (int i = 0; i < MAX_GENTITIES; ++i)
6494  {
6495  if (m_EntityHandles[i].m_NewEntity && g_entities[i].inuse)
6496  {
6497  if (g_entities[i].think != script_mover_spawn)
6498  {
6499  m_EntityHandles[i].m_NewEntity = false;
6500  Bot_Event_EntityCreated(&g_entities[i]);
6501  }
6502  }
6503  }
6504  //SendDeferredGoals();
6506  // Call the libraries update.
6507  g_BotFunctions.pfnUpdate();
6509  }
6510 }

6520  case WP_MORTAR2_SET:

6522 #ifndef LEGACY

6531 
6533 const char *_GetEntityName(gentity_t *_ent)
6534 {
6535  // For goal names.
6536  //if(_ent)
6537  //{
6538  // if(_ent->scriptName)
6539  // return _ent->scriptName;
6540  // else if(_ent->targetname)
6541  // return _ent->targetname;
6542  // else if(_ent->message)
6543  // return _ent->message;
6544  //}
6545  static char newentname[256];
6546  char *name;
6547 
6548  newentname[0] = '\0';
6549 
6550  if (_ent)
6551  {
6552  if (_ent->inuse && _ent->client)
6553  {
6554  if (_ent->client->pers.netname[0])
6555  {
6556  return _ent->client->pers.netname;
6557  }
6558  else
6559  {
6560  static char userinfo[MAX_INFO_STRING] = { 0 };
6561  trap_GetUserinfo(_ent - g_entities, userinfo, sizeof(userinfo));
6562  return Info_ValueForKey(userinfo, "name");
6563  }
6564  }
6565 
6566  if (_ent->track)
6567  {
6568  Q_strncpyz(newentname, _ent->track, sizeof(newentname));
6569  }
6570  else if (_ent->scriptName)
6571  {
6572  Q_strncpyz(newentname, _ent->scriptName, sizeof(newentname));
6573  }
6574  else if (_ent->targetname)
6575  {
6576  Q_strncpyz(newentname, _ent->targetname, sizeof(newentname));
6577  }
6578  else if (_ent->message)
6579  {
6580  Q_strncpyz(newentname, _ent->message, sizeof(newentname));
6581  }
6582 
6583  name = newentname;
6584 
6585  Q_CleanStr(name);
6586  if (name)
6587  {
6588  char undschar[] = { '-', (char)NULL };
6589  char skipchar[] = { '[', ']', '#', '!', '*', '`',
6590  '^', '&', '<', '>', '+', '=','|', '\'', '%',
6591  '.', ':', '/', '(', ')', (char)NULL };
6592  char *curchar = NULL;
6593  char *tmp;
6594  char *tmpdst;
6595  tmp = name;
6596  tmpdst = name;
6597 
6598  while (*tmp)
6599  {
6600  curchar = undschar;
6601  while (*curchar)
6602  {
6603  if (*tmp == *curchar)
6604  {
6605  *tmp = '_';
6606  break;
6607  }
6608  curchar++;
6609  }
6610  curchar = skipchar;
6611  while (*curchar)
6612  {
6613  if (*tmp == *curchar)
6614  {
6615  tmp++;
6616  break;
6617  }
6618  curchar++;
6619  }
6620  *tmpdst = *tmp;
6621  tmp++;
6622  tmpdst++;
6623  }
6624 
6625  *tmpdst = '\0';
6626 
6627  if (!Q_stricmpn("the ", name, 4))
6628  {
6629  return name + 4;
6630  }
6631 
6632  return name;
6633  }
6634  }
6635  return NULL;
6636 }
6638 qboolean Bot_Util_CheckForSuicide(gentity_t *ent)
6639 {
6640  if (ent && ent->client)
6641  {
6642  // Omni-bot: used for class changes, bot will /kill 2 seconds before spawn
6643  if (ent->client->sess.botSuicide == qtrue)
6644  {
6645  if (ent->client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_AXIS)
6646  {
6647  if ((g_redlimbotime.integer - ((level.dwRedReinfOffset + level.timeCurrent - level.startTime) % g_redlimbotime.integer)) < 2000)
6648  {
6649  Cmd_Kill_f(ent);
6650  ent->client->sess.botSuicide = qfalse;
6651  return qtrue;
6652  }
6653  }
6654  else if (ent->client->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_ALLIES)
6655  {
6656  if ((g_bluelimbotime.integer - ((level.dwBlueReinfOffset + level.timeCurrent - level.startTime) % g_bluelimbotime.integer)) < 2000)
6657  {
6658  Cmd_Kill_f(ent);
6659  ent->client->sess.botSuicide = qfalse;
6660  return qtrue;
6661  }
6662  }
6663  }
6664  }
6665  return qfalse;
6666 }

6701 void Bot_Event_AddWeapon(int _client, int _weaponId)
6702 {
6703  if (IsOmnibotLoaded())
6704  {
6705  if (IsBot(&g_entities[_client]))
6706  {
6708  int AddWeapon = _weaponId;
6709  switch (AddWeapon)
6710  {
6711  case ET_WP_GARAND:
6712  {
6713  if (COM_BitCheck(g_entities[_client].client->ps.weapons, WP_GARAND_SCOPE))
6714  {
6715  // remove the unscoped to give the scoped
6716  Event_RemoveWeapon d = { ET_WP_GARAND };
6717  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendEvent(_client, MessageHelper(MESSAGE_REMOVEWEAPON, &d, sizeof(d)));
6718 
6719  AddWeapon = ET_WP_GARAND_SCOPE;
6720  }
6721  break;
6722  }
6723  case ET_WP_K43:
6724  {
6725  if (COM_BitCheck(g_entities[_client].client->ps.weapons, WP_K43_SCOPE))
6726  {
6727  // remove the unscoped to give the scoped
6728  Event_RemoveWeapon d = { ET_WP_K43 };
6729  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendEvent(_client, MessageHelper(MESSAGE_REMOVEWEAPON, &d, sizeof(d)));
6730 
6731  AddWeapon = ET_WP_K43_SCOPE;
6732  }
6733  break;
6734  }
6735  case ET_WP_FG42:
6736  {
6737  if (COM_BitCheck(g_entities[_client].client->ps.weapons, WP_FG42SCOPE))
6738  {
6739  // remove the unscoped to give the scoped
6740  Event_RemoveWeapon d = { ET_WP_FG42 };
6741  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendEvent(_client, MessageHelper(MESSAGE_REMOVEWEAPON, &d, sizeof(d)));
6742 
6743  AddWeapon = ET_WP_FG42_SCOPE;
6744  }
6745  break;
6746  }
6747  case ET_WP_GARAND_SCOPE:
6748  {
6749  // remove the unscoped
6750  Event_RemoveWeapon d = { ET_WP_GARAND };
6751  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendEvent(_client, MessageHelper(MESSAGE_REMOVEWEAPON, &d, sizeof(d)));
6752 
6753  break;
6754  }
6755  case ET_WP_K43_SCOPE:
6756  {
6757  // remove the unscoped
6758  Event_RemoveWeapon d = { ET_WP_K43 };
6759  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendEvent(_client, MessageHelper(MESSAGE_REMOVEWEAPON, &d, sizeof(d)));
6760 
6761  break;
6762  }
6763  case ET_WP_FG42_SCOPE:
6764  {
6765  // remove the unscoped
6766  Event_RemoveWeapon d = { ET_WP_FG42 };
6767  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendEvent(_client, MessageHelper(MESSAGE_REMOVEWEAPON, &d, sizeof(d)));
6768 
6769  break;
6770  }
6771  }
6773 
6774  Event_AddWeapon d = { AddWeapon };
6775  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendEvent(_client, MessageHelper(MESSAGE_ADDWEAPON, &d, sizeof(d)));
6776  }
6777  }
6778 }

7085 void Bot_Event_EntityCreated(gentity_t *pEnt)
7086 {
7087  if (pEnt && IsOmnibotLoaded())
7088  {
7089  // Get common properties.
7090  const int iEntNum = pEnt - g_entities;
7091  GameEntity ent = HandleFromEntity(pEnt);
7092  int iClass = g_InterfaceFunctions->GetEntityClass(ent);
7093 
7094  if (iClass)
7095  {
7096  Event_EntityCreated d;
7097  d.m_Entity = GameEntity(iEntNum, m_EntityHandles[iEntNum].m_HandleSerial);
7098 
7099  d.m_EntityClass = iClass;
7100  g_InterfaceFunctions->GetEntityCategory(ent, d.m_EntityCategory);
7101  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendGlobalEvent(MessageHelper(GAME_ENTITYCREATED, &d, sizeof(d)));
7102  m_EntityHandles[iEntNum].m_Used = true;
7103  }
7104 
7105  Bot_Util_CheckForGoalEntity(ent);
7106  }
7107 
7109  // Cache smoke bombs
7110  if (pEnt && pEnt->s.eType == ET_MISSILE && pEnt->s.weapon == WP_SMOKE_BOMB)
7111  {
7112  for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SMOKEGREN_CACHE; ++i)
7113  {
7114  if (!g_SmokeGrenadeCache[i])
7115  {
7116  g_SmokeGrenadeCache[i] = pEnt;
7117  break;
7118  }
7119  }
7120  }
7121 }
7122 
7123 extern "C"
7124 {
7125 void Bot_Queue_EntityCreated(gentity_t *pEnt)
7126 {
7127  if (pEnt)
7128  {
7129  m_EntityHandles[pEnt - g_entities].m_NewEntity = true;
7130  }
7131 }
7132 void Bot_Event_EntityDeleted(gentity_t *pEnt)
7133 {
7134  if (pEnt)
7135  {
7136  const int iEntNum = pEnt - g_entities;
7137  if (IsOmnibotLoaded())
7138  {
7139  Event_EntityDeleted d = { GameEntity(iEntNum, m_EntityHandles[iEntNum].m_HandleSerial) };
7140  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendGlobalEvent(MessageHelper(GAME_ENTITYDELETED, &d, sizeof(d)));
7141  }
7142  m_EntityHandles[iEntNum].m_Used = false;
7143  m_EntityHandles[iEntNum].m_NewEntity = false;
7144  while (++m_EntityHandles[iEntNum].m_HandleSerial == 0)
7145  {
7146  }
7147  }
7148  for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SMOKEGREN_CACHE; ++i)
7149  {
7150  if (g_SmokeGrenadeCache[i] == pEnt)
7151  {
7152  g_SmokeGrenadeCache[i] = NULL;
7153  }
7154  }
7155 }

7159 void Bot_Util_SendTrigger(gentity_t *_ent, gentity_t *_activator, const char *_tagname, const char *_action)

7167  g_BotFunctions.pfnSendTrigger(triggerInfo);
7168  }

7180  }

7183 void Bot_AddFallenTeammateGoals(gentity_t *_teammate, int _team)
7184 {

7186  {
7187  Bot_Util_AddGoal("revive", _teammate, (1 << ET_TEAM_AXIS), _GetEntityName(_teammate));

7189  else if (_team == TEAM_ALLIES)
7190  {
7191  Bot_Util_AddGoal("revive", _teammate, (1 << ET_TEAM_ALLIES), _GetEntityName(_teammate));
7192  }
7193 }
